1
00:00:07,315 --> 00:00:15,122

2
00:00:15,798 --> 00:00:30,408


3
00:00:37,287 --> 00:00:41,246
黑暗已经降临 我们无法避免
These are dark times, there is no denying.

4
00:00:41,860 --> 00:00:47,492
也许 我们的世界正在经历前所未有的危机
Our world has, perhaps, faced no greater threat than it does today.

5
00:00:48,466 --> 00:00:52,425
但是我想告诉公众:
But I say this to our citizenry:

6
00:00:52,604 --> 00:00:56,506
我们 作为公仆...
We, ever your servants...

7
00:00:56,675 --> 00:00:59,337
将会保护你们的自由...
will continue to defend your liberty...

8
00:00:59,511 --> 00:01:03,845
我们要与邪恶势力斗争到底
and repel the forces that seek to take it from you.

9
00:01:05,050 --> 00:01:10,317
魔法部仍然...
Your Ministry remains...

10
00:01:10,855 --> 00:01:12,823
坚不可摧
strong.

11
00:01:17,734 --> 00:01:19,790
预言家日报: 黑魔标记 邪恶再现

12
00:01:22,887 --> 00:01:27,951
麻瓜家庭被灭门

13
00:01:30,175 --> 00:01:32,370
赫敏 茶煮好了 亲爱的
Hermione. Tea's ready, darling.

14
00:01:32,544 --> 00:01:34,478
这就来 妈妈
Coming, Mom.

15
00:01:38,416 --> 00:01:40,316
快点 达力 快一点
Come on, Dudley, hurry up.

16
00:01:40,485 --> 00:01:43,511
我们为什么一定要走
I still don't understand why we have to leave.

17
00:01:43,688 --> 00:01:48,455
因为这里对我们来说太危险了
Because, unh, it's not safe for us here anymore.

18
00:02:03,842 --> 00:02:08,211
罗恩 叫你爸回来吃晚饭
Ron, tell your father supper's nearly ready.

19
00:02:13,218 --> 00:02:14,947
这是澳大利亚吗?
Is this in Australia?

20
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,088
看起来真棒 不是吗?
Looks wonderful, doesn't it?

21
00:02:17,255 --> 00:02:22,124
沿着澳大利亚的东海岸绵延三千五百公里
Three and a half thousand kilometers along Australia's east coast.

22
00:02:23,428 --> 00:02:24,952
一忘皆空
Obliviate.

23
00:03:32,432 --> 00:03:44,250
哈利波特与死亡圣器 上

24
00:04:39,297 --> 00:04:40,958
西弗勒斯
Severus.

25
00:04:41,132 --> 00:04:44,499
我以为你迷路了呢
I was beginning to worry you had lost your way.

26
00:04:44,669 --> 00:04:48,127
快坐下 我们给你留了位置
Come, we've saved you a seat.

27
00:04:52,577 --> 00:04:53,908
我相信你又带来好消息了 是吗?
You bring news, I trust?

28
00:04:54,078 --> 00:04:57,741
他们会在下个周六行动 日落时分
It will happen Saturday next, at nightfall.

29
00:04:57,916 --> 00:05:00,282
我听到的消息恰恰相反 主人
I've heard differently, my Lord.

30
00:05:00,451 --> 00:05:03,579
傲罗德力士透露说波特...
Dawlish, the Auror, has let slip that the Potter boy...

31
00:05:03,755 --> 00:05:06,849
会在本月三十日才动身
will not be moved until the 30th of this month.

32
00:05:07,292 --> 00:05:08,554
也就是在他十七岁生日前一天
The day before he turns 17.

33
00:05:08,726 --> 00:05:11,957
你的消息错了
This is a false trail.

34
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:16,794
傲罗已经不再负责保护哈利波特
The Auror Office no longer plays any part in the protection of Harry Potter.

35
00:05:16,968 --> 00:05:21,337
他们认为魔法部已被我们渗透了
Those closest to him believe we have infiltrated the Ministry.

36
00:05:21,940 --> 00:05:23,532
还真被他们猜中了 是吧?
Well, they got that right, haven't they?

37
00:05:28,012 --> 00:05:30,480
你有什么要说的 皮尔斯?
What say you, Pius?

38
00:05:34,018 --> 00:05:36,612
我也是一头雾水 主人
One hears many things, my Lord.

39
00:05:36,788 --> 00:05:39,348
搞不清谁说的是真话
Whether the truth is among them is not clear.

40
00:05:39,524 --> 00:05:42,891
哈哈 你说话还真像政客
Heh. Spoken like a true politician.

41
00:05:43,061 --> 00:05:46,121
皮尔斯 你应该证明一下自己的价值了
You will, I think, prove most useful, Pius.

42
00:05:49,734 --> 00:05:52,965
- 那孩子会被带到哪里?  - 安全的地方
- Where will he be taken, the boy?  - To a safe house.

43
00:05:53,371 --> 00:05:55,999
有可能是凤凰社成员的家里
Most likely the home of someone in the Order.

44
00:05:56,174 --> 00:05:59,405
我听说那里已经戒备森严
I'm told it's been given every manner of protection possible.

45
00:05:59,577 --> 00:06:03,172
一旦他到了那儿 我们就束手无策了
Once there, it will be impractical to attack him.

46
00:06:03,348 --> 00:06:08,285
主人 我自愿前去完成这个任务
Ahem. My Lord. I'd like to volunteer myself for this task.

47
00:06:08,453 --> 00:06:09,442
我想亲手解决那孩子
I want to kill the boy.

48
00:06:10,788 --> 00:06:12,016
虫尾巴!
Wormtail!

49
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:15,159
我没告诉过你让客人安静点吗?
Have I not spoken to you about keeping our guest quiet?

50
00:06:15,326 --> 00:06:17,226
是的 主人
Yes, my Lord.

51
00:06:17,395 --> 00:06:20,057
马上好 主人
Right away, my Lord.

52
00:06:20,298 --> 00:06:24,792
虽然我很欣赏你嗜血成性 贝拉特里克斯...
As inspiring as I find your bloodlust, Bellatrix...

53
00:06:25,236 --> 00:06:28,535
但是我必须亲手杀了哈利波特
I must be the one to kill Harry Potter.

54
00:06:31,009 --> 00:06:35,810
但是我遇到了一个很棘手的问题
But I face an unfortunate complication.

55
00:06:35,980 --> 00:06:41,179
我的魔杖和波特的魔杖有相同的杖芯
That my wand and Potter's share the same core.

56
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:48,984
就像是双胞胎
They are, in some ways, twins.

57
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:53,859
我们可以伤害对方 但是无法杀死对方
We can wound, but not fatally harm one another.

58
00:06:55,466 --> 00:06:58,264
如果我想要杀了他...
If I am to kill him...

59
00:06:58,937 --> 00:07:02,703
那我就必须用别人的魔杖
I must do it with another's wand.

60
00:07:04,709 --> 00:07:10,409
我想你们之中肯定有人愿意把魔杖奉献给我吧?
Come, surely one of you would like the honor?

61
00:07:12,016 --> 00:07:13,677
是吗?
Mm?

62
00:07:15,386 --> 00:07:20,187
你说呢 卢修斯?
What about you, Lucius?

63
00:07:22,694 --> 00:07:24,093
主人 您是说?
My Lord?

64
00:07:24,262 --> 00:07:26,230
又装傻了?
"My Lord?"

65
00:07:27,298 --> 00:07:30,927
我需要你的魔杖
I require your wand.

66
00:07:44,248 --> 00:07:46,716
这是榆木做的吧?
Do I detect elm?

67
00:07:46,884 --> 00:07:48,852
是的 主人
Yes, my Lord.

68
00:07:54,792 --> 00:07:57,727
那杖芯呢?
And the core?

69
00:07:57,895 --> 00:08:00,090
是龙的...
Dragon. Ahem.

70
00:08:00,264 --> 00:08:01,891
是龙的心脏腱索 主人
Dragon heartstring, my Lord.

71
00:08:02,066 --> 00:08:04,261
- 龙的心脏腱索  - 是的
- Dragon heartstring.  - Mm.

72
00:08:19,984 --> 00:08:21,747
也许有些人还不知道...
To those of you who do not know...

73
00:08:21,919 --> 00:08:24,581
今晚我们还邀请了凯瑞迪・布巴吉女士...
we are joined tonight by Miss Charity Burbage...

74
00:08:24,756 --> 00:08:30,251
她此前一直在霍格沃茨任教
who, until recently, taught at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry.

75
00:08:30,428 --> 00:08:33,886
负责教授麻瓜研究课程
Her specialty was Muggle Studies.

76
00:08:37,101 --> 00:08:43,370
布巴吉女士相信我们与麻瓜并无太大差别
It is Miss Burbage's belief that Muggles are not so different from us.

77
00:08:43,541 --> 00:08:47,170
她的理论是 让我们...
She would, given her way...

78
00:08:47,945 --> 00:08:49,879
与麻瓜们一起生活
have us mate with them.

79
00:08:53,551 --> 00:08:59,751
对她来说 麻瓜与巫师结合并不是什么丢脸的事...
To her, the mixture of magical and Muggle blood is not an abomination...

80
00:08:59,924 --> 00:09:02,950
而是应该鼓励的事
but something to be encouraged.

81
00:09:04,028 --> 00:09:05,893
西弗勒斯
Severus.

82
00:09:06,064 --> 00:09:08,032
西弗勒斯 救救我
Severus, please.

83
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:11,861
我们是朋友
We're friends.

84
00:09:16,641 --> 00:09:18,199
阿瓦达索命!
Avada Kedavra!

85
00:09:28,453 --> 00:09:30,478
纳吉尼
Nagini.

86
00:09:34,092 --> 00:09:35,753
去吃晚餐吧
Dinner.

87
00:11:21,065 --> 00:11:24,466
- 嘿 哈利  - 你们终于来了
- Hello, Harry.  - All right. Wow.

88
00:11:24,635 --> 00:11:25,727
嘿
Hello.

89
00:11:25,903 --> 00:11:28,804
- 你看起来精神不错嘛  - 他看起来意气风发
- You're looking fit.  - Yeah, he's absolutely gorgeous.

90
00:11:28,973 --> 00:11:31,441
不如我们再等等好让人来干掉他吧?
What say we get undercover before someone murders him?

91
00:11:31,609 --> 00:11:32,633
晚上好
Evening.

92
00:11:37,548 --> 00:11:39,948
金斯莱 你不用保护麻瓜首相吗
Kingsley, I thought you were looking after the Prime Minister.

93
00:11:40,117 --> 00:11:42,017
你比他更重要
You are more important.

94
00:11:42,186 --> 00:11:45,246
- 很高兴见到你 哈利 我是比尔・韦斯莱  - 我也很高兴见到你
- Hello, Harry. Bill Weasley.  - Oh. Pleasure to meet you.

95
00:11:45,423 --> 00:11:48,415
- 他以前可没这么帅  - 超丑的
- He was never always this handsome.  - Dead ugly.

96
00:11:48,593 --> 00:11:49,992
那是真的
True enough.

97
00:11:50,161 --> 00:11:52,686
全拜狼人所赐 他叫格雷伯克
Owe it all to a werewolf, name of Greyback.

98
00:11:52,863 --> 00:11:56,230
- 真希望有天能让他血债血偿  - 在我心里你就是最美的 威廉
- Hope to repay the favor one day.  - You're still beautiful to me, William.

99
00:11:56,601 --> 00:12:00,230
一定要记住 芙蓉 比尔吃牛排最好煎得嫩一点
Just remember, Fleur, Bill takes his steaks on the raw side now.

100
00:12:00,404 --> 00:12:02,736
我老公 总是那么有趣
My husband, the joker.

101
00:12:02,907 --> 00:12:06,172
顺便说一句 你们一定听说了 莱姆斯和我...
By the way, wait till you hear the news. Remus and I...

102
00:12:06,344 --> 00:12:08,778
行了行了 我们之后有的是时间闲聊
All right. We'll have time for a cozy catch-up later.

103
00:12:08,946 --> 00:12:11,915
我们必须马上离开这儿 马上
We've got to get the hell out of here. And soon.

104
00:12:12,583 --> 00:12:15,848
波特 你年纪还没到 也就意味着你身上仍有踪丝
Potter, you're underage, which means you've still got the Trace on you.

105
00:12:12,583 --> 00:12:16,848
{\an8}踪丝 魔法部用来监控未成年巫师施法的手段 巫师满17岁后自动消失

106
00:12:16,020 --> 00:12:17,044
什么踪丝?
What's the Trace?

107
00:12:17,221 --> 00:12:19,883
你打个喷嚏 魔法部都知道是谁给你擦的鼻子
If you sneeze, the Ministry will know who wipes your nose.

108
00:12:20,057 --> 00:12:23,220
必须采取不用魔法的方式转移你:
We have to use those means of transport the Trace can't detect:

109
00:12:23,394 --> 00:12:25,726
骑扫帚 夜骐什么的 两人一组
Brooms, Thestrals and the like. We go in pairs.

110
00:12:25,896 --> 00:12:29,662
这样 如果有人在外面守株待兔 肯定有...
That way, if anyone's out there waiting for us, and I reckon there will be...

111
00:12:29,834 --> 00:12:32,325
他们也不知道哪个哈利・波特才是真的
they won't know which Harry Potter is the real one.

112
00:12:32,770 --> 00:12:33,930
什么叫真的?
The real one?

113
00:12:35,273 --> 00:12:38,367
我想这药水你应该不陌生吧
I believe you're familiar with this particular brew.

114
00:12:38,542 --> 00:12:40,840
不 绝对不要
No. Absolutely not.

115
00:12:41,012 --> 00:12:42,343
我说吧 他不会同意的
I told you he'd take it well.

116
00:12:42,513 --> 00:12:45,641
不 我不想大家为我一个人冒生命危险 我...
No, if you think I'm gonna let everyone risk their lives for me, I...

117
00:12:45,816 --> 00:12:48,876
- 我们又不是没干过 是吗?  - 不不 这次不一样
- Never done that before, have we?  - No. No. This is different.

118
00:12:49,053 --> 00:12:51,044
我是说 喝了药水变成我 这不行
I mean, taking that, becoming me. No.

119
00:12:51,222 --> 00:12:53,053
哥们 你以为我们愿意变成你
Well, none of us really fancy it, mate.

120
00:12:53,224 --> 00:12:57,388
万一出问题 我们可就终身变成你那小鸡仔样了
Imagine if something went wrong, and we ended up a scrawny, specky git forever.

121
00:12:57,561 --> 00:12:59,222
我们每个人都成年了 波特
Everyone here is of age, Potter.

122
00:12:59,930 --> 00:13:01,363
他们都愿意冒这个险
They've all agreed to take the risk.

123
00:13:02,733 --> 00:13:05,634
准确的说 我是被强迫的
Technically, I've been coerced.

124
00:13:05,803 --> 00:13:07,998
蒙顿格斯・弗莱奇 波特先生
Mundungus Fletcher, Mr. Potter.

125
00:13:08,172 --> 00:13:10,732
- 久仰大名今日终得一见  - 闭嘴 蒙顿格斯
- Always been a huge admirer.  - Nip it, Mundungus.

126
00:13:12,043 --> 00:13:14,534
好了 格兰杰 按照事前商定的
All right, Granger, as discussed.

127
00:13:14,712 --> 00:13:17,442
- 轻点 赫敏  - 劳驾把头发放进来
- Blimey, Hermione.  - Straight in here, if you please.

128
00:13:27,291 --> 00:13:31,489
还没尝过复方汤剂的人 给你们一个忠告
For those of you who haven't taken Polyjuice Potion before, fair warning:

129
00:13:31,662 --> 00:13:33,289
这味道像妖精尿
It tastes like goblin piss.

130
00:13:33,464 --> 00:13:36,433
看来你常喝啊 疯眼汉
Have a lot of experiences with that, do you, Mad-Eye?

131
00:13:37,335 --> 00:13:40,270
我只是缓和一下气氛
Just trying to diffuse the tension.

132
00:13:41,305 --> 00:13:43,102
噢
Oh.

133
00:13:46,177 --> 00:13:47,940
呃
Ugh.

134
00:14:12,203 --> 00:14:14,262
哇 一模一样
Wow, we're identical.

135
00:14:14,438 --> 00:14:15,496
这还不算
Not yet, you're not.

136
00:14:19,176 --> 00:14:21,736
你除了运动衫就不穿别的衣服吗?
Haven't got anything a bit more sporting, have you?

137
00:14:21,912 --> 00:14:23,379
这颜色看起来好丑
I don't really fancy this color.

138
00:14:23,547 --> 00:14:26,345
行了 赶快穿上 你现在不是你 给我闭嘴赶快换衣服
Well, fancy this, you're not you. So shut it and strip.

139
00:14:26,517 --> 00:14:28,075
好的好的 遵命
All right, all right.

140
00:14:28,252 --> 00:14:29,810
你也要换衣服 波特
You'll need to change too, Potter.

141
00:14:30,321 --> 00:14:32,949
比尔 别看我 好丑
Bill, look away. I'm hideous.

142
00:14:33,124 --> 00:14:35,422
金妮还说你有纹身呢
I knew she was lying about that tattoo.

143
00:14:35,593 --> 00:14:38,027
哈利 你视力实在太糟了
Harry, your eyesight really is awful.

144
00:14:38,195 --> 00:14:41,892
好了 现在我们要分组 每个波特都有一个护卫
Right, then. We'll be pairing off. Each Potter will have a protector.

145
00:14:42,066 --> 00:14:45,365
蒙顿格斯 你跟着我 我得看着你
Mundungus, stick tight to me. I wanna keep an eye on you.

146
00:14:45,903 --> 00:14:47,734
- 那么哈利...  - 啊?
- As for Harry...  - Yes?

147
00:14:48,572 --> 00:14:49,971
真的哈利
The real Harry.

148
00:14:50,141 --> 00:14:52,507
- 你到底是哪一个?  - 我在这儿
- Where the devil are you, anyway?  - Here.

149
00:14:52,676 --> 00:14:54,644
你和海格一起
You'll ride with Hagrid.

150
00:14:54,812 --> 00:14:59,840
我十六年前带你来这里的时候你还没一个护树罗锅大呢
I brought you here 16 years ago when you were no bigger than a Bowtruckle.

151
00:15:00,017 --> 00:15:02,918
看来带你离开这儿的人也就我最合适了
Seems only right that I should be the one to take you away now.

152
00:15:03,087 --> 00:15:06,022
是的 的确很感人 我们出发
Yes, it's all very touching. Let's go.

153
00:15:19,336 --> 00:15:23,238
方向陋居 我们在那里集合
Head for the Burrows. We'll rendezvous there.

154
00:15:23,774 --> 00:15:25,833
我数三下
On the count of three.

155
00:15:26,010 --> 00:15:27,739
坐稳了 哈利
Hold tight, Harry.

156
00:15:27,912 --> 00:15:29,709
一...
One...

157
00:15:30,581 --> 00:15:32,378
二...
two...

158
00:15:38,789 --> 00:15:40,586
三!
three!

159
00:16:10,588 --> 00:16:13,751
- 是哪一个?  - 你在哪儿?
- Which one?  - Where are you?

160
00:16:14,959 --> 00:16:16,688
他在你右边!
He's on your right!

161
00:16:16,861 --> 00:16:18,488
他在那边!
He's over there!

162
00:16:18,662 --> 00:16:20,323
在下面!
Down!

163
00:16:25,803 --> 00:16:27,464
海格 我们得回去帮他们!
Hagrid, we have to help the others!

164
00:16:27,872 --> 00:16:30,773
不行 哈利 疯眼汉的命令
I can't do that, Harry. Mad-Eye's orders.

165
00:16:37,715 --> 00:16:39,512
抓紧了
Hang on.

166
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:45,379
昏昏倒地!
Stupefy!

167
00:16:59,103 --> 00:17:00,195
坐稳了 哈利
Hang on, Harry.

168
00:17:10,114 --> 00:17:11,979
海格
Hagrid.

169
00:17:29,199 --> 00:17:31,463
不 不
No. No.

170
00:17:53,557 --> 00:17:55,548
哈利
Harry.

171
00:19:15,506 --> 00:19:18,566
哈利 海格
Harry. Hagrid.

172
00:19:19,977 --> 00:19:23,435
怎么样了? 其他人在哪里?
What happened? Where are the others?

173
00:19:23,614 --> 00:19:24,774
还没有人回来吗?
Is no one else back?

174
00:19:24,948 --> 00:19:28,509
我们是一起出发的 莫丽 他们可能还要一会儿
They were on us right from the start, Molly. We didn't stand a chance.

175
00:19:28,686 --> 00:19:31,849
谢天谢地你们两个没事
Well, thank goodness you two are all right.

176
00:19:32,022 --> 00:19:34,582
食死徒伏击了我们
The Death Eaters were waiting for us. It was an ambush.

177
00:19:34,758 --> 00:19:37,158
罗恩和唐克斯早该到了
Ron and Tonks should've already been back.

178
00:19:37,327 --> 00:19:38,521
老爸和弗雷德也该到了
Dad and Fred as well.

179
00:19:41,465 --> 00:19:43,126
来搭把手!
Here!

180
00:19:43,767 --> 00:19:47,203
快点进屋
Quick. Into the house.

181
00:19:50,874 --> 00:19:52,933
哦 宝贝儿
Oh, my boy.

182
00:19:55,112 --> 00:19:57,603
怎么会这样
Oh. Oh.

183
00:19:59,216 --> 00:20:00,513
- 卢平!  - 你要干嘛?
- Lupin!  - What are you doing?

184
00:20:03,053 --> 00:20:05,988
你第一次到我在霍格沃茨的办公室...
What creature sat in the corner...

185
00:20:06,156 --> 00:20:09,455
办公室的角落里是什么生物?
the first time Harry Potter visited my office in Hogwarts?

186
00:20:09,626 --> 00:20:11,253
- 你疯了吗?  - 什么生物?!
- Are you mad?  - What creature?!

187
00:20:11,428 --> 00:20:13,259
是一只格林迪洛
A Grindylow.

188
00:20:19,603 --> 00:20:21,264
我们被出卖了
We've been betrayed.

189
00:20:21,438 --> 00:20:23,838
伏地魔知道你在今晚动身
Voldemort knew you were being moved tonight.

190
00:20:24,007 --> 00:20:26,908
我必须弄清你是不是奸细
I had to make sure you weren't an impostor.

191
00:20:34,051 --> 00:20:35,484
站住
Wait.

192
00:20:38,489 --> 00:20:43,017
阿不思・邓布利多跟我俩说的最后一句话是什么?
The last words Albus Dumbledore spoke to the pair of us?

193
00:20:44,828 --> 00:20:49,197
"哈利是我们最宝贵的希望 相信他"
"Harry is the best hope we have. Trust him."

194
00:20:53,737 --> 00:20:54,829
你怎么逃出来的?
What gave you away?

195
00:20:55,005 --> 00:20:58,202
我想是海德薇 她想要保护我
Hedwig, I think. She was trying to protect me.

196
00:21:14,758 --> 00:21:15,918
谢谢
Thanks.

197
00:21:16,093 --> 00:21:18,254
他配得上你 他很聪明
Deserves that. Brilliant, he was.

198
00:21:18,428 --> 00:21:21,522
- 没有他我不可能活着到这儿  - 真的吗?
- I wouldn't be standing here without him.  - Really?

199
00:21:22,533 --> 00:21:25,195
至于这么惊讶吗
Always the tone of surprise.

200
00:21:33,410 --> 00:21:34,604
我们是最后一队?
We the last back?

201
00:21:35,913 --> 00:21:36,937
乔治在哪里?
Where's George?

202
00:21:58,235 --> 00:22:00,465
你感觉怎么样 乔治?
How you feeling, Georgie?

203
00:22:02,472 --> 00:22:03,996
仙乐飘飘啊
Saint-like.

204
00:22:05,209 --> 00:22:06,437
你说什么?
Come again?

205
00:22:07,377 --> 00:22:10,938
动听啊
Saint-like. I'm holy.

206
00:22:11,448 --> 00:22:14,508
瞧 这有个洞 洞听 弗雷德 懂了吗?
I'm holey, Fred. Get it?

207
00:22:16,320 --> 00:22:21,019
耳朵的俏皮话多得是 你偏偏挑了"洞听"
The whole wide world of ear-related humor and you go for "I'm holey."

208
00:22:21,191 --> 00:22:22,351
真够可怜的
That's pathetic.

209
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:25,258
就算这样我还是比你帅
Reckon I'm still better-looking than you.

210
00:22:28,799 --> 00:22:30,994
疯眼汉死了
Mad-Eye's dead.

211
00:22:41,378 --> 00:22:45,109
蒙顿格斯一看到伏地魔就幻影移形了
Mundungus took one look at Voldemort and Disapparated.

212
00:23:08,038 --> 00:23:10,063
方向陋居
Head for the Burrows.

213
00:23:10,874 --> 00:23:12,239
这真是难以置信
This is beyond anything I imagined.

214
00:23:12,409 --> 00:23:15,037
- 七个?  - 七个...? 魂器
- Seven?  - Seven...? A Horcrux.

215
00:23:15,212 --> 00:23:16,645
他们可能被藏在任何地方
They could be hidden anywhere.

216
00:23:16,813 --> 00:23:19,008
为了把灵魂分成七块...
To rip the soul into seven pieces....

217
00:23:19,182 --> 00:23:22,151
- 如果你摧毁了所有魂器...  - 你就击败了了伏地魔
- If you did destroy each Horcrux....  - One destroys Voldemort.

218
00:23:25,756 --> 00:23:27,383
相信我
Trust me.

219
00:23:28,325 --> 00:23:31,886
你骗了我 骗了我 奥利凡德
You lied to me. Lied to me, Ollivander.

220
00:24:03,827 --> 00:24:05,761
要去哪里?
Going somewhere?

221
00:24:09,433 --> 00:24:13,529
不能再有人为我而死了
Nobody else is going to die. Not for me.

222
00:24:13,704 --> 00:24:15,501
为你?
For you?

223
00:24:15,672 --> 00:24:17,902
你觉得疯眼汉是为你而死的?
You think Mad-Eye died for you?

224
00:24:18,075 --> 00:24:21,010
你觉得乔治负伤也是为了你?
You think George took that curse for you?

225
00:24:21,778 --> 00:24:25,714
也许你真是救世之星 但这一切远比你重要得多
You may be the Chosen One, mate, but this is a whole lot bigger than that.

226
00:24:25,882 --> 00:24:28,407
一直比你想的重要得多
It's always been bigger than that.

227
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:33,111
- 跟我一起走  - 什么 撇下赫敏?
- Come with me.  - What, and leave Hermione?

228
00:24:33,590 --> 00:24:37,822
你疯了吗? 没有她我们两天都活不下去
You mad? We wouldn't last two days without her.

229
00:24:39,229 --> 00:24:40,753
别告诉她是我说的
Don't tell her I said that.

230
00:24:42,332 --> 00:24:45,529
再说了 你身上的踪丝还没失效
Besides, you've still got the Trace on you.

231
00:24:45,702 --> 00:24:49,798
- 我们还要参加婚礼呢...  - 什么见鬼婚礼
- We've still got the wedding...  - I don't care about a wedding.

232
00:24:49,973 --> 00:24:54,842
对不起 无意冒犯 但是我们必须开始找魂器了
I'm sorry. No matter whose it is. I have to start finding these Horcruxes.

233
00:24:55,012 --> 00:24:56,980
那是我们唯一可以击倒他的方法...
They're our only chance to beat him...

234
00:24:57,147 --> 00:25:00,116
我们等得越久 他就越强大
and the longer we stay here, the stronger he gets.

235
00:25:01,551 --> 00:25:03,644
今晚不是时候 兄弟
Tonight's not the night, mate.

236
00:25:03,954 --> 00:25:06,422
就当让他多活两天吧
We'd only be doing him a favor.

237
00:25:34,184 --> 00:25:36,118
你觉得他知道吗?
Do you think he knows?

238
00:25:36,853 --> 00:25:42,723
魂器 就是他一部分的灵魂 也就是他的一部分
I mean, they're bits of his soul, these Horcruxes. Bits of him.

239
00:25:43,460 --> 00:25:47,726
当邓布利多摧毁了他的戒指 你毁掉了汤姆・里德尔的日记...
When Dumbledore destroyed the ring, you destroyed Tom Riddle's diary...

240
00:25:49,232 --> 00:25:51,826
他肯定察觉到了
he must have felt something.

241
00:25:52,602 --> 00:25:56,333
要毁灭其他魂器 我们必须先找到它们
To kill the other Horcruxes, we have to find them.

242
00:25:56,706 --> 00:25:58,674
它们在哪儿?
Where are they?

243
00:25:59,209 --> 00:26:01,268
我们从哪里开始?
Where do we start?

244
00:26:04,714 --> 00:26:05,806
准备好了吗
Ready when you are.

245
00:26:07,551 --> 00:26:11,851
注意点! 这是哥哥的婚礼 打起精神来
Please pay attention! It's your brother's wedding. Buck up.

246
00:26:12,651 --> 00:26:17,280
邓布利多的黑暗秘密 丽塔・斯基特新书发布

247
00:26:29,272 --> 00:26:33,530
悼念邓布利多 埃菲亚斯・多吉

248
00:26:37,280 --> 00:26:39,339
帮我拉一下拉链 好吗?
Zip me up, will you?

249
00:26:53,196 --> 00:26:55,130
挺傻的 是吧 这婚礼?
It seems silly, doesn't it, a wedding?

250
00:26:55,632 --> 00:26:57,998
对将来的事视而不见
Given everything that's going on.

251
00:26:59,336 --> 00:27:01,395
也许这就是最好的理由...
Maybe that's the best reason to have it...

252
00:27:02,005 --> 00:27:04,530
该来的总会要来的
because of everything that's going on.

253
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:22,751
早上好
Morning.

254
00:27:32,936 --> 00:27:35,097
准备好 要升起来咯
Come on, keep up.

255
00:27:35,772 --> 00:27:37,433
大家一起来
All together now.

256
00:27:37,607 --> 00:27:43,045
一 二 三
One, two, three.

257
00:27:53,123 --> 00:27:55,557
那边看起来怎么样 孩子们?
How's it looking at your end, boys?

258
00:27:56,193 --> 00:27:58,127
很不错
Brilliant.

259
00:28:00,230 --> 00:28:05,065
见鬼 魔法部长来这里干什么?
Bloody hell. What's the Minister of Magic doing here?

260
00:28:10,974 --> 00:28:12,839
什么风把你吹来了 部长先生?
To what do we owe the pleasure, Minister?

261
00:28:13,009 --> 00:28:17,571
我想我们彼此都很清楚为什么 波特先生
I think we both know the answer to that question, Mr. Potter.

262
00:28:25,255 --> 00:28:27,155
这个是...?
And this is...?

263
00:28:35,198 --> 00:28:39,100
"我将要呈上的是..."
"Herein is set forth the last will and testament...

264
00:28:39,269 --> 00:28:43,865
阿不思・珀西瓦尔・伍尔弗里克・布赖恩・邓布利多的遗嘱以及遗物
of Albus Percival Wulfric Brian Dumbledore.

265
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:48,500
首先 我留给罗纳德・比利尔斯・韦斯莱的...
First, to Ronald Bilius Weasley...

266
00:28:48,678 --> 00:28:51,977
是我的熄灯器...
I leave my Deluminator...

267
00:28:52,148 --> 00:28:54,412
我亲手制作的...
a device of my own making...

268
00:28:54,584 --> 00:28:59,817
希望可以在最黑暗的时候...
in the hope that, when things seem most dark...

269
00:29:01,458 --> 00:29:04,325
为他指明方向"
it will show him the light."

270
00:29:10,233 --> 00:29:13,327
- 邓布利多留给我的?  - 是的
- Dumbledore left this for me?  - Yeah.

271
00:29:14,271 --> 00:29:15,863
好棒啊
Brilliant.

272
00:29:16,906 --> 00:29:18,737
这有什么用?
What is it?

273
00:29:30,887 --> 00:29:32,479
真牛
Wicked.

274
00:29:34,791 --> 00:29:37,760
"我留给赫敏・简・格兰杰...
"To Hermione Jean Granger...

275
00:29:37,927 --> 00:29:43,092
这本"诗翁彼豆故事集"...
I leave my copy of The Tales of Beedle the Bard...

276
00:29:43,266 --> 00:29:47,930
希望她在里面读到欢乐与启示"
in the hope that she find it entertaining and instructive."

277
00:29:48,738 --> 00:29:50,069
我妈妈以前常给我念这本书
Mom used to read me those.

278
00:29:50,940 --> 00:29:52,464
"巫师与大礼帽"
"The Wizard and the Hopping Pot."

279
00:29:52,642 --> 00:29:55,577
"小兔芭比迪和咯咯笑树桩"
"Babbitty Rabbitty and the Cackling Stump."

280
00:29:57,347 --> 00:30:00,714
不是吧 小兔芭比迪
Come on, Babbitty Rabbitty.

281
00:30:01,184 --> 00:30:02,879
没听说过?
No?

282
00:30:03,219 --> 00:30:06,017
"我留给哈利・詹姆・波特...
"To Harry James Potter...

283
00:30:06,556 --> 00:30:10,287
他第一次在霍格沃茨魁地奇比赛上抓到的飞贼...
I leave the Snitch he caught in his first Quidditch match at Hogwarts...

284
00:30:10,460 --> 00:30:15,488
希望他能记住通过坚毅与技巧...
as a reminder of the rewards of perseverance...

285
00:30:17,734 --> 00:30:19,929
得来的一切"
and skill."

286
00:30:39,989 --> 00:30:43,049
- 就这个 没别的了?  - 那倒不是
- Is that it, then?  - Not quite.

287
00:30:43,226 --> 00:30:48,630
邓布利多还给你留了第二样东西:
Dumbledore left you a second bequest:

288
00:30:48,865 --> 00:30:51,857
戈德里克・格兰芬多之剑
The sword of Godric Gryffindor.

289
00:30:53,470 --> 00:30:58,066
不幸的是 邓布利多没有权利将格兰芬多之剑送给他人
Unfortunately, the sword of Gryffindor was not Dumbledore's to give away.

290
00:30:58,475 --> 00:31:01,205
作为一件重要的历史文物 它属于...
As an important historical artifact, it belongs...

291
00:31:01,378 --> 00:31:02,470
属于哈利
To Harry.

292
00:31:03,313 --> 00:31:05,247
它是属于哈利的
It belongs to Harry.

293
00:31:05,415 --> 00:31:08,111
当哈利在密室里需要它的时候格兰芬多之剑就出现了
It came to him when he needed it in the Chamber of Secrets.

294
00:31:08,284 --> 00:31:11,185
出色的格兰芬多巫师都可以召唤出宝剑
The sword may present itself to any worthy Gryffindor.

295
00:31:11,354 --> 00:31:13,686
但不能说剑是他的私人物品
That does not make it that wizard's property.

296
00:31:15,125 --> 00:31:18,754
而且 现在这把剑已经不知去向
And, in any event, the current whereabouts of the sword are unknown.

297
00:31:18,928 --> 00:31:21,522
- 什么?  - 那把剑失踪了
- Excuse me?  - The sword is missing.

298
00:31:22,899 --> 00:31:26,426
我不知道你想要干什么 波特先生...
I don't know what you're up to, Mr. Potter...

299
00:31:26,603 --> 00:31:30,562
但是你不能独自面对
but you can't fight this war on your own.

300
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:33,140
他太强大了
He's too strong.

301
00:32:34,337 --> 00:32:35,599
哈利
Hello, Harry.

302
00:32:36,506 --> 00:32:40,499
我是不是打扰到你了? 我从你眼中看到你在思考
I've interrupted a deep thought, haven't I? I can see it growing smaller in your eyes.

303
00:32:40,677 --> 00:32:42,201
当然没有 近来好吗 卢娜?
Of course not. How are you, Luna?

304
00:32:42,378 --> 00:32:45,006
我很好 刚刚被一个地精咬了
Very well. Got bitten by a garden gnome only moments ago.

305
00:32:45,181 --> 00:32:47,513
地精口水对身体有好处
Gnome saliva is very beneficial.

306
00:32:47,684 --> 00:32:50,050
谢诺菲留斯・洛夫古德 我们就住在山那边
Xenophilius Lovegood. We live just over the hill.

307
00:32:50,220 --> 00:32:51,414
很高兴认识你 先生
Pleasure to meet you, sir.

308
00:32:51,588 --> 00:32:54,352
相信你有所耳闻 波特先生 我们唱唱反调杂志...
I trust you know, Mr. Potter, that we at The Quibbler...

309
00:32:54,524 --> 00:32:56,856
不像那些预言家日报的马屁精...
unlike those toadies at The Daily Prophet...

310
00:32:57,026 --> 00:32:59,620
邓布利多在世时我们支持他...
fully supported Dumbledore in his lifetime...

311
00:32:59,796 --> 00:33:03,459
他死后 我们依然全力支持他
and, in his death, support you just as fully.

312
00:33:03,766 --> 00:33:05,131
谢谢你
Thank you.

313
00:33:05,301 --> 00:33:08,134
走了 爸爸 哈利现在不想和我们说话
Come, Daddy. Harry doesn't want to talk to us right now.

314
00:33:08,304 --> 00:33:10,602
他只是出于礼貌没有说而已
He's just too polite to say so.

315
00:33:10,773 --> 00:33:12,832
哈利・波特
Harry Potter.

316
00:33:16,379 --> 00:33:18,506
抱歉 先生? 我能坐这里吗?
Excuse me, sir? May I sit down?

317
00:33:18,681 --> 00:33:22,082
哦 波特先生 当然可以 请坐
Mr. Potter. By all means. Here.

318
00:33:22,252 --> 00:33:23,913
谢谢
Thanks.

319
00:33:26,623 --> 00:33:29,922
您在预言家日报的文章很感人
I found what you wrote in The Daily Prophet really moving.

320
00:33:30,493 --> 00:33:33,291
你一定和邓布利多是老相识了
You obviously knew Dumbledore well.

321
00:33:33,463 --> 00:33:36,398
的确 我和他算是认识时间最长的了
Well, I certainly knew him the longest.

322
00:33:36,566 --> 00:33:39,296
如果不算他的弟弟阿不福思的话...
That is, if you don't count his brother, Aberforth...

323
00:33:39,469 --> 00:33:42,495
当然 从来也没有人把阿不福思算进去
and somehow, people never do seem to count Aberforth.

324
00:33:42,839 --> 00:33:44,898
- 我不知道他还有一个弟弟  - 很正常
- I didn't even know he had a brother.  - Ah.

325
00:33:45,074 --> 00:33:48,635
邓布利多一直是一个很谨慎的人 从小就这样
Well, Dumbledore was always very private, even as a boy.

326
00:33:48,811 --> 00:33:50,210
别泄气 埃菲亚斯
Don't despair, Elphias.

327
00:33:50,380 --> 00:33:54,817
我听说丽塔・斯基特把他的一切都公之于众了...
I'm told he's been thoroughly unriddled by Rita Skeeter...

328
00:33:54,984 --> 00:33:57,817
绝对不少于八百页
in 800 pages, no less.

329
00:33:58,454 --> 00:34:02,857
据说有人找她聊过
Word has it that someone talked to her.

330
00:34:03,026 --> 00:34:05,824
一个对邓布利多一家很了解的人
Someone who knew the Dumbledore family well.

331
00:34:06,229 --> 00:34:09,824
你我心里都清楚这人是谁 埃菲亚斯
Both you and I know who that is, Elphias.

332
00:34:09,999 --> 00:34:11,466
一个可怕的叛徒
A monstrous betrayal.

333
00:34:13,369 --> 00:34:14,961
这是在说谁?
Who are we talking about?

334
00:34:16,439 --> 00:34:18,566
巴希达・巴沙特
Bathilda Bagshot.

335
00:34:20,243 --> 00:34:21,301
- 谁?  - 天啊 孩子...
- Who?  - My God, boy...

336
00:34:21,477 --> 00:34:26,244
她是上世纪最著名的魔法史学家
She's only the most celebrated magical historian of the last century.

337
00:34:27,951 --> 00:34:32,183
没有人比她和邓布利多一家关系更密切了
She was as close to the Dumbledores as anyone.

338
00:34:32,355 --> 00:34:37,383
丽塔・斯基特肯定不辞辛苦去了戈德里克山谷...
Oh, I'm sure Rita Skeeter thought it well worth a trip to Godric's Hollow...

339
00:34:37,560 --> 00:34:40,757
就为了刺探他家的陈年往事
to take a peek into that old bird's rattled cage.

340
00:34:40,930 --> 00:34:42,761
戈德里克山谷?
Godric's Hollow?

341
00:34:43,199 --> 00:34:45,099
巴希达・巴沙特住在戈德里克山谷?
Bathilda Bagshot lives at Godric's Hollow?

342
00:34:45,501 --> 00:34:47,594
那是她和邓布利多初遇的地方
Well, that's where she first met Dumbledore.

343
00:34:47,770 --> 00:34:49,635
你是说邓布利多也住在那?
You don't mean to say he lived there too?

344
00:34:49,806 --> 00:34:53,367
在他父亲杀了那三个麻瓜之后 他们就举家搬去那了
The family moved there after his father killed those three Muggles.

345
00:34:53,543 --> 00:34:57,172
当时这桩丑闻闹得沸沸扬扬的
Oh, it was quite the scandal.

346
00:34:57,347 --> 00:35:02,182
老实说 孩子 你确定你真的了解他吗?
Honestly, my boy, are you sure you knew him at all?

347
00:35:28,645 --> 00:35:31,739
魔法部已被攻陷
The Ministry has fallen.

348
00:35:32,382 --> 00:35:36,284
魔法部长也已死去
The Minister of Magic is dead.

349
00:35:38,755 --> 00:35:41,053
他们来了
They are coming.

350
00:35:41,224 --> 00:35:43,317
他们来了
They are coming.

351
00:35:44,594 --> 00:35:46,084
他们来了
They are coming.

352
00:35:46,262 --> 00:35:47,729
他们来了!
They're coming!

353
00:35:49,766 --> 00:35:51,597
很高兴认识你 波特先生
Nice meeting you, Mr. Potter.

354
00:36:02,679 --> 00:36:05,045
- 金妮!  - 哈利! 走!
- Ginny!  - Harry! Go!

355
00:36:05,214 --> 00:36:06,272
离开这里!
Go!

356
00:36:19,595 --> 00:36:22,189
市内观光团去不去? 十五分钟内就出发
Here you go, sightseeing tour? Leaves in 15 minutes.

357
00:36:23,633 --> 00:36:26,261
- 我们在哪?  - 沙夫茨伯里大街(英国伦敦剧场集中的街区)
- Where are we?  - Shaftesbury Avenue.

358
00:36:26,436 --> 00:36:29,633
我爸妈过去常带我来看戏
I used to come to the theater here with Mom and Dad.

359
00:36:29,939 --> 00:36:33,033
不知道我为什么会想到这里 这地方突然就跳到我脑子里来了
I don't know why I thought of it. It just popped into my head.

360
00:36:33,443 --> 00:36:35,274
这边
This way.

361
00:36:39,082 --> 00:36:41,175
我们得换一下衣服
We need to change.

362
00:36:47,123 --> 00:36:48,385
这什么情况...?
How the ruddy...?

363
00:36:48,558 --> 00:36:51,118
无痕伸展咒
Undetectable Extension Charm.

364
00:36:51,561 --> 00:36:53,825
你简直太了不起了 真的
You're amazing, you are.

365
00:36:54,030 --> 00:36:56,590
至于这么惊讶吗
Always the tone of surprise.

366
00:36:58,601 --> 00:37:00,728
啊 还好书也带了
Ah. That'll be the books.

367
00:37:06,242 --> 00:37:08,107
婚礼上其他人怎么办?
What about all the people at the wedding?

368
00:37:08,277 --> 00:37:10,745
- 我们是不是应该回去帮忙?  - 那些人是冲你来的
- Do you think we should go back?  - They were after you.

369
00:37:10,913 --> 00:37:13,074
我们回去会使大家陷入危险
We'd put everyone in danger by going back.

370
00:37:14,951 --> 00:37:16,680
- 罗恩是对的  - 喂
- Ron's right.  - Ahem.

371
00:37:16,853 --> 00:37:18,514
咖啡?
Coffee?

372
00:37:19,055 --> 00:37:22,081
- 一杯卡布奇诺 谢谢  - 你呢?
- A cappuccino, please.  - You?

373
00:37:22,925 --> 00:37:26,224
- 和她要一样的  - 我也是
- What she said.  - Same.

374
00:37:29,599 --> 00:37:33,433
我们现在去哪? 破釜酒吧?
So where do we go from here? Leaky Cauldron?

375
00:37:33,803 --> 00:37:34,895
太危险了
It's too dangerous.

376
00:37:35,805 --> 00:37:39,332
如果伏地魔已经控制了魔法部 所有我们常去的地方都不安全
If Voldemort has taken over the Ministry, none of the old places are safe.

377
00:37:39,509 --> 00:37:42,569
婚礼上所有人都会躲起来的
Everyone from the wedding will have gone underground, into hiding.

378
00:37:42,745 --> 00:37:45,236
我的包被我忘在陋居了 里面装着我所有的东西
My rucksack with all my things, I've left it at the Burrow.

379
00:37:50,386 --> 00:37:52,286
不是吧 都装进去了?
You're joking.

380
00:37:53,890 --> 00:37:57,849
我花了好几天把所有必需品都装好了 以防万一
I've had all the essentials packed for days, just in case.

381
00:37:58,027 --> 00:38:00,222
顺便说一下 这些牛仔裤不是我最喜欢的
By the way, these jeans, not my favorite.

382
00:38:01,397 --> 00:38:02,455
趴下!
Down!

383
00:38:03,599 --> 00:38:04,896
昏昏倒地!
Stupefy!

384
00:38:09,105 --> 00:38:10,834
飞沙走石!
Expulso!

385
00:38:20,750 --> 00:38:22,581
统统石化
Petrificus Totalus.

386
00:38:26,722 --> 00:38:27,780
快走
Go.

387
00:38:28,224 --> 00:38:29,384
离开这里
Leave.

388
00:38:34,063 --> 00:38:36,861
把门锁上 把灯灭掉
Lock the door, get the lights.

389
00:38:46,108 --> 00:38:47,837
他叫罗尔
This one's name is Rowle.

390
00:38:48,344 --> 00:38:51,780
斯内普在天文塔上杀死邓布利多那晚 他也在场
He was on the Astronomy Tower the night Snape killed Dumbledore.

391
00:38:52,582 --> 00:38:57,076
他是多洛霍夫 我曾见过通缉他的告示
This is Dolohov. I recognize him from the wanted posters.

392
00:38:58,154 --> 00:39:00,315
我们该怎么处置你呢?
So, what we gonna do with you, hey?

393
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:03,283
如果倒下的是我们 肯定被你杀了对吧?
Kill us if it was turned round, wouldn't you?

394
00:39:03,459 --> 00:39:04,790
如果我们杀了他们 大家都会知道我们曾在这出现
If we kill them, they'll know we were here.

395
00:39:04,961 --> 00:39:06,360
罗恩
Ron.

396
00:39:06,529 --> 00:39:10,488
如果是他杀了疯眼汉呢 你还会怜悯他吗?
Suppose he did Mad-Eye. How would you feel then?

397
00:39:12,468 --> 00:39:14,095
最好只抹去他们的记忆
It's better we wipe their memories.

398
00:39:14,971 --> 00:39:16,939
你说了算
You're the boss.

399
00:39:17,240 --> 00:39:19,003
赫敏...
Hermione...

400
00:39:21,477 --> 00:39:23,945
还是你来吧
you're the best at spells.

401
00:39:41,597 --> 00:39:43,792
一忘皆空
Obliviate.

402
00:39:56,145 --> 00:39:57,737
他们是怎么知道我们在这?
How is it they knew we were there?

403
00:39:57,914 --> 00:39:59,506
你身上的踪丝还没解除?
Maybe you still have the Trace on you?

404
00:39:59,682 --> 00:40:03,118
不可能 踪丝17岁当天就解除了 巫师法规定的
Can't be. Trace breaks at 17. It's wizarding law.

405
00:40:04,921 --> 00:40:06,479
怎么了?
What?

406
00:40:07,290 --> 00:40:10,259
我们还没给你庆祝生日呢 哈利
We didn't celebrate your birthday, Harry.

407
00:40:10,626 --> 00:40:13,891
金妮和我一起为你准备了个蛋糕
Ginny and I, we prepared a cake.

408
00:40:14,063 --> 00:40:17,032
我们本来打算在婚礼最后拿出来的
We were going to bring it out at the end of the wedding.

409
00:40:17,199 --> 00:40:20,635
你们这么贴心我很感激 不过想想咱们在几分钟前差点
I appreciate the thought, but given the fact that we were almost killed...

410
00:40:20,803 --> 00:40:23,203
被两个食死徒杀了...
by a couple of Death Eaters a few minutes ago...

411
00:40:24,874 --> 00:40:26,569
对哦
Right.

412
00:40:27,376 --> 00:40:28,400
说得也是
Perspective.

413
00:40:28,577 --> 00:40:31,569
街上人多眼杂的 我们得去个安全的地方
We need to get off the streets, get somewhere safe.

414
00:41:04,680 --> 00:41:06,705
这究竟是干什么用的?
What was that all about?

415
00:41:07,683 --> 00:41:13,519
估计是疯眼汉的主意 以防斯内普来偷窥
Probably Mad-Eye's idea, in case Snape decided to come snooping.

416
00:41:21,697 --> 00:41:23,665
从形显身
Homenum Revelio.

417
00:41:30,306 --> 00:41:32,137
这儿没别人了
We're alone.

418
00:41:38,948 --> 00:41:41,178
我以为另一只魔杖...
I believed another wand...

419
00:41:41,350 --> 00:41:43,818
- 你骗我  - 我怎么敢骗您
- You lied to me.  - It makes no sense.

420
00:41:46,655 --> 00:41:49,624
我以为再换一根魔杖就会有用 我发誓
I believed a different wand would work, I swear.

421
00:41:51,127 --> 00:41:53,186
肯定还有别的方法
There must be another way.

422
00:42:32,022 --> 00:42:39,433
小天狼星

423
00:42:58,127 --> 00:43:01,186
巴希达・巴沙特

424
00:43:02,127 --> 00:43:03,186
"魔法史"

425
00:43:03,532 --> 00:43:07,263
哈利? 赫敏 你们在哪?
Harry? Hermione, where are you?

426
00:43:07,536 --> 00:43:09,868
我觉得我发现了一些东西
I think I've found something.

427
00:43:16,178 --> 00:43:17,236
这没什么啊
Lovely.

428
00:43:22,918 --> 00:43:26,410
"雷古勒斯・阿克图勒斯・布莱克"
"Regulus Arcturus Black."

429
00:43:26,589 --> 00:43:28,284
他就是R.A.B
R.A.B.

430
00:43:31,894 --> 00:43:35,193
"在你读到这之前我早就死了
"I know I will be dead long before you read this.

431
00:43:35,364 --> 00:43:39,391
我偷走了真正的魂器 并打算尽快销毁它"
I have stolen the real Horcrux and intend to destroy it."

432
00:43:39,768 --> 00:43:42,168
R.A.B是小天狼星的弟弟?
R.A.B. is Sirius's brother?

433
00:43:42,605 --> 00:43:44,368
是的
Yes.

434
00:43:46,475 --> 00:43:50,343
问题是 他是否真的毁掉了真正的魂器?
Question is, did he actually destroy the real Horcrux?

435
00:44:12,067 --> 00:44:14,228
你一直在暗中监视我们 对吧?
You've been spying on us, have you?

436
00:44:14,403 --> 00:44:18,863
克利切只是一直看着罢了
Kreacher has been watching.

437
00:44:19,041 --> 00:44:20,975
或许他知道真正的挂坠盒在哪
Maybe he knows where the real locket is.

438
00:44:23,979 --> 00:44:25,913
你以前见过这个吗?
Have you ever seen this before?

439
00:44:26,081 --> 00:44:27,673
克利切?
Kreacher?

440
00:44:28,517 --> 00:44:30,951
这是雷古拉斯主人的挂坠盒
It's Master Regulus' locket.

441
00:44:31,120 --> 00:44:33,816
但这个挂坠盒有两个 对吗?
But there were two, weren't there?

442
00:44:34,823 --> 00:44:36,518
另一个在哪?
Where's the other one?

443
00:44:39,028 --> 00:44:43,590
克利切不知道另一个挂坠盒在哪
Kreacher doesn't know where the other locket is.

444
00:44:43,766 --> 00:44:46,166
没关系 但你有没有见过它? 它是否曾在这栋房子里?
Yes, but did you ever see it? Was it in this house?

445
00:44:46,335 --> 00:44:47,495
肮脏的泥巴种
Filthy Mudblood.

446
00:44:47,670 --> 00:44:49,365
- 食死徒会来...  - 罗恩
- Death Eaters are coming...  - Ron.

447
00:44:49,538 --> 00:44:52,371
- 叛血者 韦斯莱  - 回答她
- Blood traitor, Weasley.  - Answer her.

448
00:44:54,143 --> 00:44:56,373
是的
Yes.

449
00:44:57,413 --> 00:45:00,871
它是曾在这栋房子里
It was here in this house.

450
00:45:02,151 --> 00:45:04,483
一个邪恶至极的玩意
A most evil object.

451
00:45:04,653 --> 00:45:05,881
什么意思?
How do you mean?

452
00:45:06,655 --> 00:45:10,955
在雷古勒斯主人死前 他曾命令克利切毁了它...
Before Master Regulus died, he ordered Kreacher to destroy it...

453
00:45:11,126 --> 00:45:16,393
但无论克利切如何努力 就是做不到
but no matter how hard Kreacher tried, he could not do it.

454
00:45:16,565 --> 00:45:18,157
那东西现在在哪?
Well, where is it now?

455
00:45:18,801 --> 00:45:23,397
- 有人把它拿走了吗?  - 那个人有天晚上来到这
- Did someone take it?  - He came in the night.

456
00:45:23,572 --> 00:45:28,236
他拿走了很多东西 包括挂坠盒
He took many things, including the locket.

457
00:45:28,410 --> 00:45:29,934
谁?
Who did?

458
00:45:30,613 --> 00:45:32,205
那个人是谁 克利切?
Who was it, Kreacher?

459
00:45:34,750 --> 00:45:37,412
蒙顿格斯
Mundungus.

460
00:45:37,586 --> 00:45:41,078
蒙顿格斯・弗莱奇
Mundungus Fletcher.

461
00:45:42,157 --> 00:45:43,749
去把他找来
Find him.

462
00:45:55,157 --> 00:45:58,749
霍格沃茨特快列车

463
00:46:05,281 --> 00:46:06,748
我父亲会强烈谴责这种行为的
My father will hear about this.

464
00:46:12,054 --> 00:46:13,919
喂 笨蛋
Hey, losers.

465
00:46:14,657 --> 00:46:16,921
他不在这
He isn't here.

466
00:46:26,657 --> 00:46:29,921
头号不良分子 哈利・波特

467
00:46:30,539 --> 00:46:32,939
作为你们新的魔法部长...
As your new Minister for Magic...

468
00:46:33,142 --> 00:46:38,307
我保证会恢复这座宽容之殿...
I promise to restore this temple of tolerance...

469
00:46:38,480 --> 00:46:40,141
昔日的光彩
to its former glory.

470
00:46:40,141 --> 00:46:42,141
{\an8}魔法即强权

471
00:46:41,550 --> 00:46:43,381
因此 从今日起...
Therefore, beginning today...

472
00:46:44,453 --> 00:46:48,219
每一位员工都必须接受...
each employee will submit themselves...

473
00:46:48,891 --> 00:46:51,121
忠诚评估
for evaluation.

474
00:46:51,994 --> 00:46:54,986
如果你没有什么需要隐瞒...
You have nothing to fear...

475
00:46:56,432 --> 00:46:58,161
就没有什么需要害怕
if you have nothing to hide.

476
00:47:02,571 --> 00:47:04,163
- 多少钱?  - 两个金加隆
- How much?  - Two Galleons.

477
00:47:04,340 --> 00:47:06,831
快点 时间就是金钱 再见 伙计
Come on, time is money. Cheers, pal.

478
00:47:07,009 --> 00:47:08,943
{\an8}搜捕队: 专门追捕麻瓜出生的巫师 叛血者和逃学的学生并带到魔法部去换钱的人

479
00:47:07,009 --> 00:47:08,943
- 搜捕队来啦!  - 别挡路
- Snatchers!  - Move out of the way.

480
00:47:15,150 --> 00:47:16,617
- 我说了  - 滚开
- I told you.  - Get out.

481
00:47:16,785 --> 00:47:17,809
扁他
Squash him.

482
00:47:27,029 --> 00:47:28,656
轻点
Be a bit gentler.

483
00:47:54,757 --> 00:47:56,884
他们对肉体有记忆
They have flesh memories.

484
00:47:59,027 --> 00:48:04,556
当斯克林杰给你的时候 我以为你一碰它就会打开
When Scrimgeour first gave it to you, I thought it might open at your touch.

485
00:48:05,401 --> 00:48:08,165
露出邓布利多藏在里面的东西
That Dumbledore had hidden something inside it.

486
00:48:08,404 --> 00:48:10,065
很多人都很疑惑...
Many of you are wondering...

487
00:48:10,239 --> 00:48:13,174
为什么伏地魔还未证明他已经...
why Voldemort has yet to show himself now that he has vanquished...

488
00:48:13,342 --> 00:48:16,402
挫败他和他的追随者最大的绊脚石
the most powerful symbol of opposition to him and his followers.

489
00:48:18,447 --> 00:48:19,471
下来
Get off.

490
00:48:19,648 --> 00:48:22,412
哈利・波特 好久不见
Harry Potter, so long it's been.

491
00:48:22,885 --> 00:48:24,216
赶紧给我下来
Get off me.

492
00:48:29,825 --> 00:48:33,761
克利切奉命把这个小偷带回来了...
As requested, Kreacher has returned with the thief...

493
00:48:33,929 --> 00:48:35,920
- 除你武器  - 蒙顿格斯・弗莱奇
- Expelliarmus.  - Mundungus Fletcher.

494
00:48:36,098 --> 00:48:39,295
你搞什么鬼? 派两只该死的家养小精灵来抓我
What you playing at? Setting a pair of bleeding house-elves after me.

495
00:48:39,468 --> 00:48:40,958
多比只是想帮忙
Dobby was only trying to help.

496
00:48:41,136 --> 00:48:45,505
多比看到克利切出现在对角巷 多比十分好奇
Dobby saw Kreacher in Diagon Alley, which Dobby thought was curious.

497
00:48:45,674 --> 00:48:50,008
然后多比听到克利切提到哈利・波特的名字
And then Dobby heard Kreacher mention Harry Potter's name.

498
00:48:50,179 --> 00:48:53,012
- 我只是...  - 然后多比看到克利切...
- I just...  - And then Dobby saw Kreacher...

499
00:48:53,182 --> 00:48:55,980
- 跟这个小偷蒙顿格斯说话...  - 我不是小偷
- talking with the thief, Mundungus...  - I'm no thief.

500
00:48:56,151 --> 00:48:59,086
你这个白... 痴
You foul little... git.

501
00:48:59,488 --> 00:49:03,891
我是个奇珍异宝供应商
I'm a purveyor of rare and wondrous objects.

502
00:49:04,059 --> 00:49:05,924
你是个小偷 顿格 大家都知道
You're a thief, Dung. Everyone knows it.

503
00:49:06,094 --> 00:49:09,063
韦斯莱主人 很高兴再见到你
Master Weasley, so good to see you again.

