both believed to have been traveling with Tonks, Cresswell...

674
01:07:32,833 --> 01:07:34,357
据信已经逃脱
and Gornuk, may have escaped.

675
01:07:34,535 --> 01:07:38,301
如果迪安在收听或者任何人知道他的下落...
If Dean is listening or anyone has any knowledge of his whereabouts...

676
01:07:38,472 --> 01:07:41,532
他的父母和姐妹急切盼望他的消息
his parents and sisters are desperate for news.

677
01:07:41,709 --> 01:07:45,076
与此同时 一个麻瓜五口之家惨遭灭门
Meanwhile, a Muggle family of five has been found dead in their home.

678
01:07:45,246 --> 01:07:48,511
你知道那咒语的 哈利
You know the spell, Harry.

679
01:07:52,253 --> 01:07:53,515
告诉我
Tell me.

680
01:07:56,157 --> 01:07:57,988
告诉我 格里戈维奇
Tell me, Gregorovitch.

681
01:07:58,159 --> 01:07:59,786
它被偷走了
It was stolen from me.

682
01:07:59,961 --> 01:08:03,419
是谁? 谁偷的?
Who was he? The thief?

683
01:08:06,567 --> 01:08:10,526
是个男孩 是他偷的
It was a boy. It was he who took it.

684
01:08:10,905 --> 01:08:13,203
我再也没有见过它了
I never saw it again.

685
01:08:13,374 --> 01:08:15,171
我以性命担保
I swear on my life.

686
01:08:16,043 --> 01:08:17,203
我相信你
I believe you.

687
01:08:23,217 --> 01:08:24,946
阿瓦达索命!
Avada Kedavra!

688
01:08:39,600 --> 01:08:41,090
我以为已经停止了
I thought it had stopped.

689
01:08:43,004 --> 01:08:45,438
你不能再让他进入你思想了 哈利
You can't keep letting him in, Harry.

690
01:08:47,508 --> 01:08:50,443
神秘人找到了格里戈维奇
You-Know-Who has found Gregorovitch.

691
01:08:50,745 --> 01:08:52,303
魔杖制作人?
The wandmaker?

692
01:08:52,480 --> 01:08:57,008
他想要一样格里戈维奇曾经拥有的东西...
He wants something that Gregorovitch used to have...

693
01:08:57,184 --> 01:08:58,651
但我不知道是什么
but I don't know what.

694
01:08:58,819 --> 01:09:04,815
但他急切地想找到它 我是说 就像生死攸关一样
But he wants it desperately. I mean, it's as if his life depends on it.

695
01:09:06,360 --> 01:09:07,884
别管他
Don't.

696
01:09:08,062 --> 01:09:10,257
- 那使他感到安慰  - 广播让我很难受
- It comforts him.  - It sets my teeth on edge.

697
01:09:10,431 --> 01:09:12,661
他期望听到什么 好消息吗?
What's he expecting to hear, good news?

698
01:09:12,833 --> 01:09:15,700
长久期待的那样 魔法部的垮台令人震惊
who long expected it, the fall of the Ministry was shocking.

699
01:09:15,870 --> 01:09:18,236
我想他只是希望没有坏消息
I think he just hopes he doesn't hear bad news.

700
01:09:18,406 --> 01:09:20,340
我们保证继续充当您的耳目...
We promise to remain your eyes and ears...

701
01:09:20,508 --> 01:09:21,941
他还有多久才能走动?
How long before he can travel?

702
01:09:22,109 --> 01:09:25,306
力所能及地为您提供消息
Bringing you news when we can, from wherever we can.

703
01:09:25,479 --> 01:09:26,776
我已经竭尽所能了
I'm doing everything I can.

704
01:09:26,947 --> 01:09:28,471
你做的还不够!
You're not doing enough!

705
01:09:31,218 --> 01:09:33,243
摘掉它
Take it off.

706
01:09:34,021 --> 01:09:36,581
我说了 现在就摘掉
I said, take it off now.

707
01:09:47,601 --> 01:09:50,331
- 好些了?  - 好多了
- Better?  - Loads.

708
01:09:54,041 --> 01:09:56,305
我们轮流戴 好吗?
We'll take it in turns, okay?

709
01:10:25,372 --> 01:10:28,739
芬奇承认他的发明最近出现了纰漏
Finch does admit his invention currently has one short.

710
01:10:28,909 --> 01:10:30,376
现在 其他消息:
And now, other news:

711
01:10:30,544 --> 01:10:33,809
西弗勒斯・斯内普 新任霍格沃茨校长...
Severus Snape, newly-appointed headmaster of Hogwarts...

712
01:10:33,981 --> 01:10:37,747
宣布所有的学生必须遵守新校规
has decreed that all students must conform to the latest house rules.

713
01:11:05,379 --> 01:11:09,816
霍格沃茨与邓布利多领导下的状况相去甚远
Hogwarts bears little resemblance to the school under Dumbledore's leadership.

714
01:11:09,984 --> 01:11:13,613
斯内普的体制非常严厉 反映了黑魔头的心意...
Snape's curriculum is severe, reflecting the wishes of the Dark Lord...

715
01:11:14,455 --> 01:11:19,392
任何违规行为均由两位食死徒负责严加惩处
and infractions are dealt with harshly by the two Death Eaters on staff.

716
01:11:38,879 --> 01:11:40,210
什么东西?
What's that?

717
01:11:49,490 --> 01:11:52,254
这什么味道?
What's that smell?

718
01:12:14,715 --> 01:12:16,740
- 你干嘛呢?  - 很重啊
- What you doing?  - It's heavy.

719
01:12:16,917 --> 01:12:18,509
要不我来帮你扛好了?
Oh, sorry. Do you want me to carry it?

720
01:12:18,686 --> 01:12:21,621
- 好啊 谢谢  - 别逗了 抬起来
- Yeah, thank you.  - Don't be ridiculous. Pick it up.

721
01:12:23,190 --> 01:12:24,214
傻蛋
Numpty.

722
01:12:29,330 --> 01:12:31,321
搜捕队
Snatchers.

723
01:12:32,366 --> 01:12:34,800
幸好你的魔咒有用
Good to know your enchantments work.

724
01:12:39,840 --> 01:12:43,469
他能闻到我的香水味
He could smell it. My perfume.

725
01:12:45,679 --> 01:12:47,738
我告诉过你了...
I've told you...

726
01:12:48,215 --> 01:12:50,046
罗恩还不适合幻影显形
Ron isn't strong enough to Apparate.

727
01:12:50,217 --> 01:12:53,948
好吧 那就只能步行了
Well, then, we'll go on foot.

728
01:12:54,755 --> 01:12:59,692
还有赫敏 虽然我喜欢你的香水味 但还是别喷了
And next time, Hermione, as much as I like your perfume, just don't wear any.

729
01:13:04,598 --> 01:13:08,466
现在广播失踪的巫师们
And now for the names of missing witches and wizards.

730
01:13:09,336 --> 01:13:11,497
这些是已确认的
These are confirmed.

731
01:13:12,339 --> 01:13:15,706
谢天谢地 今日名单很短
Thankfully, the list is short today.

732
01:13:16,443 --> 01:13:18,502
邓布赖特夫妇 杰森和艾莉森
Jason and Alison Denbright.

733
01:13:19,380 --> 01:13:20,404
哦 谢谢
Oh. Thank you.

734
01:13:20,581 --> 01:13:24,312
法利一家 贝拉 杰克 查理和玛琪
Bella, Jake, Charlie, and Madge Farley.

735
01:13:24,652 --> 01:13:25,676
乔・劳里
Joe Laurie.

736
01:13:26,987 --> 01:13:29,581
埃莉诺・萨拉・吉布斯
Eleanor Sarah Gibbs.

737
01:13:30,758 --> 01:13:34,057
特里格夫妇 哈里和布朗尼
Harry and Bronwyn Trigg.

738
01:13:35,696 --> 01:13:38,722
道森夫妇 罗伯和埃莉
Rob and Ellie Dowson.

739
01:13:39,833 --> 01:13:42,358
乔治亚・克拉克戴
Georgia Clark-Day.

740
01:13:42,937 --> 01:13:45,462
约书亚・弗莱克森
Joshua Flexson.

741
01:13:45,873 --> 01:13:47,363
乔治・科塔斯
George Coutas.

742
01:13:48,509 --> 01:13:51,342
马瑟夫妇 加布里埃尔和艾米丽
Gabriella and Emily Mather.

743
01:13:52,379 --> 01:13:55,473
厄兰夫妇 雅各布和米米
Jacob and Mimi Erland.

744
01:13:56,550 --> 01:13:58,040
加拉格尔父子 威廉姆和布莱恩
William and Brian Gallagher.

745
01:13:58,218 --> 01:14:00,652
他根本不知道自己在干嘛 对吧?
He doesn't know what he's doing, does he?

746
01:14:03,490 --> 01:14:05,390
谁也不知道
None of us do.

747
01:14:07,962 --> 01:14:10,726
格里夫夫妇 托比和奥利维亚
Toby and Olivia Gleaves.

748
01:14:11,598 --> 01:14:14,226
凯里克夫妇 凯蒂和詹姆斯
Katie and James Killick.

749
01:14:14,401 --> 01:14:16,926
埃尔西・瓦伦丁・施罗德
Elsie Valentine Schroeder.

750
01:14:17,972 --> 01:14:20,065
詹妮弗・温斯顿
Jennifer Winston.

751
01:14:20,240 --> 01:14:23,334
黑里格夫妇 塔米辛和罗拉
Tamsin and Lola Hillicker.

752
01:14:24,545 --> 01:14:25,569
夏普夫妇 斯卡雷特基蒂
Scarlet and Kitty Sharp.

753
01:14:44,618 --> 01:14:46,449
天啊
Oh, my God.

754
01:14:46,821 --> 01:14:48,448
怎么了?
What?

755
01:14:49,023 --> 01:14:51,048
我一会儿告诉你
I'll tell you in a minute.

756
01:14:51,592 --> 01:14:54,288
现在就告诉我吧
Maybe you could tell me now.

757
01:14:54,662 --> 01:14:57,688
格兰芬多之剑 是妖精所制
The sword of Gryffindor, it's goblin-made.

758
01:14:57,865 --> 01:14:58,957
这谁都知道
Brilliant.

759
01:15:00,034 --> 01:15:02,434
不 你没明白
No, you don't understand.

760
01:15:02,770 --> 01:15:05,136
灰尘和铁锈对剑没有影响
Dirt and rust have no effect on the blade.

761
01:15:06,140 --> 01:15:09,507
它只吸收使之强大之物
It only takes in that which makes it stronger.

762
01:15:09,910 --> 01:15:11,275
所以呢
Okay.

763
01:15:11,445 --> 01:15:14,937
哈利 你已经销毁了一个魂器了 对吧?
Harry, you've already destroyed one Horcrux, right?

764
01:15:15,116 --> 01:15:17,380
密室里汤姆・里德尔的日记本
Tom Riddle's diary in the Chamber of Secrets.

765
01:15:17,551 --> 01:15:20,452
用的是蛇怪的毒牙 如果你告诉我...
With a Basilisk fang. If you tell me you've got one of those...

766
01:15:20,621 --> 01:15:24,079
- 你那破珠绣包里有一颗...  - 你还不懂吗?
- in that bloody beaded bag of yours...  - Don't you see?

767
01:15:24,258 --> 01:15:27,989
在密室里 你用格兰芬多剑刺中了蛇怪
In the Chamber of Secrets, you stabbed the Basilisk with the sword of Gryffindor.

768
01:15:28,162 --> 01:15:31,689
它的剑刃上浸着蛇怪的毒液
Its blade is impregnated with Basilisk venom.

769
01:15:31,866 --> 01:15:33,959
它只吸收使之强大之物
It only takes in that which makes it stronger.

770
01:15:34,135 --> 01:15:37,298
- 正是 所以...  - 它可以销毁魂器
- Exactly, which is why...  - It can destroy Horcruxes.

771
01:15:37,471 --> 01:15:39,735
所以邓布利多才在遗嘱里遗赠给你
That's why Dumbledore left it to you in his will.

772
01:15:39,907 --> 01:15:44,310
你太天才了 赫敏 真的
You are brilliant, Hermione. Truly.

773
01:15:44,478 --> 01:15:48,539
其实 我只是逻辑性强 所以我才能回顾看似无关的细节...
Actually, I'm highly logical, which allows me to look past extraneous detail...

774
01:15:48,716 --> 01:15:51,207
并看出其他人忽略的信息
and perceive clearly that which others overlook.

775
01:15:51,385 --> 01:15:54,081
- 是啊  - 当然 还有一个问题
- Yeah  - There's only one problem, of course.

776
01:15:59,460 --> 01:16:01,587
剑不见了
The sword was stolen.

777
01:16:02,997 --> 01:16:05,522
不好意思 还有个我呢
Yeah, I'm still here.

778
01:16:06,033 --> 01:16:10,163
二位请继续 别让我搅了兴致
But you two carry on. Don't let me spoil the fun.

779
01:16:11,539 --> 01:16:15,532
- 出了什么问题?  - 问题? 没有问题
- What's wrong?  - Wrong? Nothing's wrong.

780
01:16:15,709 --> 01:16:17,609
至少在你看来没有
Not according to you, anyway.

781
01:16:17,778 --> 01:16:21,407
听着 别阴阳怪气的 有话就说
Look, if you've got something to say, don't be shy. Spit it out.

782
01:16:21,782 --> 01:16:25,081
好 那我就说了 别指望我会兴高采烈...
All right, I'll spit it out. But don't expect me to be grateful...

783
01:16:25,252 --> 01:16:27,777
不就是又多了一件该死的东西要找
because there's another damn thing we've gotta find.

784
01:16:27,955 --> 01:16:30,219
我以为你知道参加的是什么行动
I thought you knew what you signed up for.

785
01:16:30,724 --> 01:16:32,589
是啊 我也以为我知道
Yeah. I thought I did too.

786
01:16:32,760 --> 01:16:35,786
那好 恕我愚钝 但我不明白您的意思
Well then, I'm sorry, but I don't quite understand.

787
01:16:35,963 --> 01:16:39,421
哪个部分没有符合你的期望呢?
What part of this isn't living up to your expectations?

788
01:16:39,600 --> 01:16:41,864
你以为我们会住在五星级饭店里?
Did you think we were gonna be staying in a five-star hotel?

789
01:16:42,036 --> 01:16:45,301
隔一天就能找到一个魂器? 以为圣诞节就能回家?
Finding a Horcrux every other day? You thought you'd be back by Christmas?

790
01:16:45,472 --> 01:16:47,303
我只是以为 这么长时间了...
I just thought, after all this time...

791
01:16:47,474 --> 01:16:50,910
我们能取得些成果 我以为你知道自己在做什么
we would've achieved something. I thought you knew what you were doing.

792
01:16:51,078 --> 01:16:53,478
我以为邓布利多告诉过你要干什么
I thought Dumbledore told you something worthwhile.

793
01:16:53,647 --> 01:16:56,844
- 我以为你有一个真正的计划  - 邓布利多说过的我都告诉你了
- I thought you had a plan.  - I told you everything Dumbledore told me.

794
01:16:57,017 --> 01:16:59,212
而且别忘了 我们找到了一个魂器
In case you haven't noticed, we found a Horcrux.

795
01:16:59,386 --> 01:17:03,254
是啊 毁灭它就跟找到剩下的魂器一样容易呢 对吧?
Yeah, and we're as close to getting rid of it as we are to finding the rest of them, aren't we?

796
01:17:03,424 --> 01:17:06,018
罗恩 拜托 摘下...
Ron. Please, take...

797
01:17:06,560 --> 01:17:08,960
摘下魂器 你戴了它一整天了...
Please take the Horcrux off. You wouldn't be saying this...

798
01:17:09,129 --> 01:17:10,460
否则你不会说这种话的
if you hadn't been wearing it all day.

799
01:17:10,631 --> 01:17:13,031
知道我每晚听广播的原因吗?
Do you know why I listen to that radio every night, dear?

800
01:17:13,200 --> 01:17:17,864
确保我没有听到金妮的名字 或者弗雷德 乔治还有妈妈
To make sure I don't hear Ginny's name, or Fred, or George or Mom.

801
01:17:18,038 --> 01:17:21,201
你以为我没在听吗? 你以为我不知道这种感觉吗?!
You think I'm not listening too? You think I don't know how this feels?!

802
01:17:21,375 --> 01:17:22,842
是 你不知道这种感觉!
No, you don't know how it feels!

803
01:17:23,010 --> 01:17:25,376
你的父母死了 你没有家庭
Your parents are dead. You have no family.

804
01:17:26,480 --> 01:17:29,210
- 住手 住手  - 好啊 那就走吧!
- Stop. Stop.  - Fine, then go!

805
01:17:30,050 --> 01:17:31,210
走啊!
Go, then!

806
01:17:34,121 --> 01:17:35,145
走啊
Fine.

807
01:17:38,292 --> 01:17:39,953
罗恩
Ron.

808
01:17:43,197 --> 01:17:44,994
你呢?
And you?

809
01:17:46,734 --> 01:17:49,259
跟我走还是留下来?
Are you coming or you staying?

810
01:17:56,377 --> 01:17:59,437
很好 我懂了
Fine. I get it.

811
01:18:00,080 --> 01:18:02,048
那天晚上我都看见了
I saw you two the other night.

812
01:18:02,449 --> 01:18:04,883
罗恩 那是... 你误会了
Ron, that's... that's nothing.

813
01:18:07,021 --> 01:18:08,386
罗恩...
Ron...

814
01:18:11,592 --> 01:18:13,924
罗恩 你去哪?
Ron, where are you going?

815
01:18:14,928 --> 01:18:17,158
求你了 回来
Please, come back.

816
01:18:18,632 --> 01:18:20,327
罗恩
Ron.

817
01:18:25,039 --> 01:18:26,063
罗恩!
Ron!

818
01:19:28,369 --> 01:19:30,997
平安镇守
Salvio Hexia.

819
01:19:34,475 --> 01:19:36,909
驱逐麻瓜
Repellum Muggletum.

820
01:19:39,980 --> 01:19:42,414
平安镇守
Salvio Hexia.

