834
01:21:05,098 --> 01:21:08,465
# 嗨 小火车啊 等等我 #
# Hey, little train, wait for me #

835
01:21:08,669 --> 01:21:12,503
# 我曾如此盲目 但如今我已明了 #
# I once was blind but now I see #

836
01:21:12,673 --> 01:21:16,006
# 你是否还为我留有一隅? #
# Have you left a seat for me? #

837
01:21:16,176 --> 01:21:20,306
# 这是否是我想入非非? #
# Is that such a stretch of the imagination? #

838
01:21:20,481 --> 01:21:23,814
# 嗨 小火车啊 等等我 #
# Hey, little train, wait for me #

839
01:21:23,984 --> 01:21:27,852
# 我曾被束缚 但如今又是自由之身 #
# I was held in chains but now I'm free #

840
01:21:28,155 --> 01:21:31,056
# 我依然坚守 你可曾看见? #
# I'm hanging in there. Don't you see? #

841
01:21:31,225 --> 01:21:35,685
# 在这历尽考验的旅程中 #
# In this process of elimination #

842
01:21:35,863 --> 01:21:38,991
# 嗨 小火车啊 我们跳上的小火车 #
# Hey, little train, we're jumping on #

843
01:21:39,233 --> 01:21:42,691
# 它将行驶在那天国之路 #
# The train that goes to the kingdom #

844
01:21:43,303 --> 01:21:46,602
# 我们很幸福 妈妈 我们很开心 #
# We're happy, Ma, we're having fun #

845
01:21:46,773 --> 01:21:50,675
# 这超越我最狂野的渴望 #
# It's beyond my wildest expectation #

846
01:21:50,844 --> 01:21:54,075
# 嗨 小火车啊 我们跳上的小火车 #
# Hey, little train, we're jumping on #

847
01:21:54,248 --> 01:21:57,877
# 它将行驶在那天国之路 #
# The train that goes to the kingdom #

848
01:21:58,418 --> 01:22:01,615
# 我们很幸福 妈妈 我们很开心 #
# We're happy, Ma, we're having fun #

849
01:22:01,788 --> 01:22:06,657
# 哪怕这火车尚未离站 #
# The train ain't even left the station #

850
01:22:48,988 --> 01:22:51,957
我在结束之时开启

851
01:22:53,373 --> 01:22:54,863
赫敏
Hermione.

852
01:22:55,042 --> 01:22:57,374
赫敏? 你是对的
Hermione? You were right.

853
01:22:57,544 --> 01:22:59,102
金色飞贼有肉体记忆...
Snitches have flesh memories...

854
01:22:59,279 --> 01:23:03,909
但这个飞贼不是我用手抓住的 我差点吞了它
but I didn't catch the first Snitch with my hand, I almost swallowed it.

855
01:23:09,189 --> 01:23:11,953
- "我在结束之时开启"  - 你觉得这什么意思?
- "I open at the close."  - What do you think that means?

856
01:23:12,125 --> 01:23:13,524
我不知道
I don't know.

857
01:23:15,929 --> 01:23:18,329
我也有发现
I found something as well.

858
01:23:24,705 --> 01:23:28,163
一开始我以为这是一只眼睛 但我现在不这么想了
At first I thought it was an eye, but now I don't think it is.

859
01:23:28,342 --> 01:23:32,506
这不是如尼文 它也不在"魔法字音表"里
It isn't a rune, and it isn't anywhere in Spellman's Syllabary.

860
01:23:32,980 --> 01:23:36,074
某人用墨水写的 它不是书里的 有人画上去的
Somebody inked it in. It isn't part of the book. Somebody drew it.

861
01:23:36,249 --> 01:23:39,912
卢娜的爸爸在比尔和芙蓉的婚礼上戴着这个标志
Luna's dad was wearing that at Bill and Fleur's wedding.

862
01:23:42,656 --> 01:23:45,955
为什么把它画在一本儿童书里?
Why would someone draw it in a children's book?

863
01:23:48,562 --> 01:23:50,996
听着 赫敏 我一直在考虑
Look, Hermione, I've been thinking.

864
01:23:51,565 --> 01:23:53,658
我想去戈德里克山谷
I want to go to Godric's Hollow.

865
01:23:53,834 --> 01:23:56,894
那是我出生的地方 也是我父母死亡的地方
It's where I was born. It's where my parents died.

866
01:23:57,070 --> 01:24:00,665
正因为它对你意义重大 所以他肯定期待你去那里
That's exactly where he'll expect you to go because it means something to you.

867
01:24:00,841 --> 01:24:03,275
没错 但那里对他也有特殊意义 赫敏
Yeah, but it means something to him too, Hermione.

868
01:24:03,443 --> 01:24:05,434
神秘人差点死在那儿
You-Know-Who almost died there.

869
01:24:05,612 --> 01:24:10,276
我是说 那不正是他可能藏魂器的理想之地吗?
I mean, isn't that exactly the type of place he'd be likely to hide a Horcrux?

870
01:24:11,251 --> 01:24:13,811
太危险了 哈利
It's dangerous, Harry.

871
01:24:15,422 --> 01:24:19,415
但我不得不承认 我也一直想着我们必须得去
But even I have to admit, recently I've been thinking we'll have to go there.

872
01:24:19,593 --> 01:24:22,027
我觉得可能有其他东西藏匿于此
I think it's possible something else is hidden there.

873
01:24:22,195 --> 01:24:23,719
什么?
What?

874
01:24:24,431 --> 01:24:26,126
那把剑
The sword.

875
01:24:26,700 --> 01:24:30,500
如果邓布利多希望你找到它 但又不想它落入魔法部之手...
If Dumbledore wanted you to find it, but didn't want it in the Ministry's hands...

876
01:24:30,671 --> 01:24:34,869
还有哪里比格兰芬多创建人出生地更合适的呢?
where better to hide it than the birthplace of the founder of Gryffindor?

877
01:24:36,209 --> 01:24:38,074
赫敏...
Hermione....

878
01:24:43,316 --> 01:24:46,046
别再让我给你剪头发了
Don't ever let me give you a haircut again.

879
01:25:07,307 --> 01:25:09,969
我仍然觉得应该用复方汤剂的
I still think we should've used Polyjuice Potion.

880
01:25:10,143 --> 01:25:11,667
不
No.

881
01:25:12,345 --> 01:25:14,540
这是我出生的地方
This is where I was born.

882
01:25:14,881 --> 01:25:17,281
我不想以别人的身份回来
I'm not returning as someone else.

883
01:25:27,094 --> 01:25:30,086
晚安 哈哈哈
Good night. Ha-ha-ha.

884
01:25:33,133 --> 01:25:35,897
哈利 我想今天是平安夜
Harry, I think it's Christmas Eve.

885
01:25:37,404 --> 01:25:38,701
你听
Listen.

886
01:25:44,411 --> 01:25:47,244
你觉得他们也葬在这里吗 赫敏?
Do you think they'd be in there, Hermione?

887
01:25:47,681 --> 01:25:49,672
我的父母
My mom and dad.

888
01:25:55,622 --> 01:25:57,886
嗯 我觉得在
Yeah, I think they would.

889
01:26:34,461 --> 01:26:37,521
"伊格诺图斯・佩弗利尔"
"Ignotus Peverell."

890
01:26:39,599 --> 01:26:41,226
嘿 哈利?
Hey, Harry?

891
01:26:48,299 --> 01:26:50,226
詹姆・波特 莉莉・波特

892
01:27:19,105 --> 01:27:21,300
圣诞快乐 赫敏
Merry Christmas, Hermione.

893
01:27:22,609 --> 01:27:24,839
圣诞快乐 哈利
Merry Christmas, Harry.

894
01:27:44,698 --> 01:27:50,102
哈利 有人在看我们 教堂那边
Harry, there's someone watching us. By the church.

895
01:28:00,814 --> 01:28:02,645
我想我知道那是谁
I think I know who that is.

896
01:28:04,517 --> 01:28:05,950
我不喜欢这样 哈利
I don't like this, Harry.

897
01:28:06,119 --> 01:28:11,147
赫敏 她认识邓布利多 剑可能在她那儿
Hermione, she knew Dumbledore. She might have the sword.

898
01:28:30,010 --> 01:28:31,637
这是他们被害的地方 赫敏
This is where they died, Hermione.

899
01:28:39,219 --> 01:28:41,687
他杀害他们的地方
This is where he murdered them.

900
01:28:54,200 --> 01:28:56,134
你是巴希达 对吗?
You're Bathilda, aren't you?

901
01:29:01,741 --> 01:29:03,834
来 我来帮你
Here, let me do that.

902
01:29:27,968 --> 01:29:31,870
巴沙特女士 这个人是谁?
Miss Bagshot, who is this man?

903
01:29:43,483 --> 01:29:45,144
哈利
Harry.

904
01:29:49,189 --> 01:29:51,054
荧光闪烁
Lumos.

905
01:30:08,699 --> 01:30:10,754
"亲爱的巴蒂 多谢您的帮助 您说出了一切 即使您现在已不记得了 丽塔"

906
01:30:17,799 --> 01:30:20,554
"羽毛笔之后"丽塔・斯基特又一力作 "阿不思・邓布利多的生平和谎言"

907
01:31:31,424 --> 01:31:32,448
哈利!
Harry!

908
01:32:23,276 --> 01:32:24,334
霹雳爆炸!
Confringo!

909
01:33:07,086 --> 01:33:09,213
感觉好些了吗?
Are you feeling better?

910
01:33:12,292 --> 01:33:14,760
这次你又超越自己了 赫敏
You've outdone yourself this time, Hermione.

911
01:33:14,928 --> 01:33:17,021
迪安森林
The Forest of Dean.

912
01:33:17,997 --> 01:33:22,366
我曾和爸妈来过一次 好多年前了
I came here once with Mom and Dad, years ago.

913
01:33:23,002 --> 01:33:25,129
和我记忆中一模一样
It's just how I remember it.

914
01:33:25,538 --> 01:33:29,474
树木 河流 所有的一切
The trees, the river, everything.

915
01:33:29,776 --> 01:33:32,609
就像从未改变
Like nothing's changed.

916
01:33:33,846 --> 01:33:36,838
当然这不是真的 一切都变了
Not true, of course. Everything's changed.

917
01:33:37,817 --> 01:33:41,617
如果现在把我父母带来 他们可能根本不记得了
If I brought my parents back here now, they probably wouldn't recognize any of it.

918
01:33:43,723 --> 01:33:47,853
不记得这树木 河流...
Not the trees, not the river...

919
01:33:49,629 --> 01:33:51,756
甚至于我
not even me.

920
01:33:56,903 --> 01:33:59,701
或许我们应该留在这里 哈利
Maybe we should just stay here, Harry.

921
01:34:01,708 --> 01:34:03,835
慢慢变老
Grow old.

922
01:34:09,849 --> 01:34:13,148
你想知道照片里的男孩是谁
You wanted to know who the boy in the photograph was.

923
01:34:13,886 --> 01:34:14,978
我知道
I know.

924
01:34:16,155 --> 01:34:18,555
他叫盖勒特・格林德沃
Gellert Grindelwald.

925
01:34:25,498 --> 01:34:28,899
他是我在格里戈维奇魔杖店里见到的小偷
He's the thief I saw in Gregorovitch's Wand Shop.

926
01:34:29,068 --> 01:34:32,333
说到这里 我的魔杖呢?
Speaking of which, where is my wand?

927
01:34:33,673 --> 01:34:36,073
我的魔杖呢 赫敏?
Where's my wand, Hermione?

928
01:34:44,717 --> 01:34:49,211
我们离开戈德里克山谷的时候 我施的咒反弹了
As we were leaving Godric's Hollow, I cast a curse and it rebounded.

929
01:34:51,958 --> 01:34:53,186
抱歉
I'm sorry.

930
01:34:53,860 --> 01:34:56,488
- 我试图修好它 但魔杖不同其他  - 就这样吧
- I tried to mend it, but wands are different.  - It's done.

931
01:34:58,464 --> 01:35:02,423
把你的给我 进去暖暖吧
Leave me yours. Go inside and get warm.

932
01:35:02,835 --> 01:35:05,167
挂坠也给我戴
I'll take the locket as well.

933
01:35:17,717 --> 01:35:19,082
相信我
Trust me.

934
01:36:44,837 --> 01:36:46,464
荧光闪烁
Lumos.

935
01:37:27,547 --> 01:37:28,912
宝剑飞来
Accio sword.

936
01:37:34,754 --> 01:37:36,654
四分五裂
Diffindo.

937
01:39:17,089 --> 01:39:20,252
- 赫敏?  - 你疯了吗?
- Hermione?  - Are you mental?

938
01:39:21,460 --> 01:39:23,018
是你?
It was you?

939
01:39:23,195 --> 01:39:26,961
是啊 很明显嘛
Well, yeah. Bit obvious, I think.

940
01:39:27,133 --> 01:39:28,930
母鹿也是你召唤的 是吗?
And you cast the doe as well, did you?

941
01:39:29,502 --> 01:39:33,165
- 不是 我以为是你  - 不是 我的守护神是牡鹿
- No, I thought that was you.  - No, my Patronus is a stag.

942
01:39:33,339 --> 01:39:35,534
啊 对 有角
Right. Yeah. Antlers.

943
01:39:38,711 --> 01:39:41,874
好了 罗恩 动手吧
Okay, Ron. Do it.

944
01:39:42,848 --> 01:39:46,579
我不行 这东西对我的影响大过对你和赫敏
I can't handle it. That thing affects me more than it affects you and Hermione.

945
01:39:47,119 --> 01:39:49,747
- 更应如此  - 不行 我做不到
- All the more reason.  - No. I can't.

946
01:39:49,922 --> 01:39:51,150
那你为什么在这儿?
Then why are you here?

947
01:39:52,558 --> 01:39:54,617
你为什么回来?
Why did you come back?

948
01:40:02,201 --> 01:40:06,331
现在 我必须说话让它打开 等打开了 不要犹豫
Now, I'll have to speak to it in order for it to open. When it does, don't hesitate.

949
01:40:06,939 --> 01:40:09,464
我不知道里面是什么 但它肯定会奋力抵抗
I don't know what's in there, but it'll put up a fight.

950
01:40:09,642 --> 01:40:12,338
日记本里的里德尔碎片想杀了我
The bit of Riddle that was in that diary tried to kill me.

951
01:40:14,814 --> 01:40:16,441
好吧
All right.

952
01:40:17,283 --> 01:40:18,841
一...
One...

953
01:40:19,518 --> 01:40:20,576
二...
two...

954
01:40:21,253 --> 01:40:23,153
三
three.

955
01:40:33,399 --> 01:40:38,496
我窥见你的内心 而它是我的
I have seen your heart, and it is mine.

956
01:40:41,107 --> 01:40:45,009
我眼见你的梦境 罗纳德・韦斯莱...
I have seen your dreams, Ronald Weasley...

957
01:40:45,177 --> 01:40:47,577
我也知晓你的恐惧
and I have seen your fears.

958
01:40:49,281 --> 01:40:53,445
最不受母亲宠爱 她渴望一个女儿
Least loved by your mother, who craved a daughter.

959
01:40:54,086 --> 01:40:59,080
最不受女友喜爱 她更喜欢你的朋友
Least loved by the girl who prefers your friend.

960
01:40:59,258 --> 01:41:01,988
罗恩 杀了它!
Ron, kill it!

961
01:41:08,434 --> 01:41:11,130
我们没你更好
We were better without you.

962
01:41:11,637 --> 01:41:13,366
没你更开心
Happier without you.

963
01:41:13,539 --> 01:41:18,909
跟哈利・波特比起来谁会看你一眼?
Who could look at you compared to Harry Potter?

964
01:41:20,146 --> 01:41:23,479
跟救世之星比起来你算什么?
What are you compared with the Chosen One?

965
01:41:23,649 --> 01:41:24,809
罗恩 它在撒谎!
Ron, it's lying!

966
01:41:24,984 --> 01:41:27,976
你母亲亲口说更希望我做她的儿子
Your mother confessed she would have preferred me as a son.

967
01:41:28,154 --> 01:41:31,146
哪个女人会看上你?
What woman would take you?

968
01:41:31,357 --> 01:41:34,520
你一无是处
You are nothing.

969
01:41:34,694 --> 01:41:35,820
一文不值
Nothing.

970
01:41:36,595 --> 01:41:40,622
跟他比更是云泥之别
Nothing compared to him.

971
01:42:31,183 --> 01:42:32,844
还好...
Just think...

972
01:42:33,753 --> 01:42:35,846
只剩下三个了
only three to go.

973
01:42:38,891 --> 01:42:40,620
赫敏?
Hermione?

974
01:42:42,895 --> 01:42:44,624
赫敏?
Hermione?

975
01:42:49,168 --> 01:42:51,102
没事吧?
Is everything all right?

976
01:42:51,737 --> 01:42:56,401
没事 而且 别没事好得多了
It's fine. Actually, you know, it's more than fine.

977
01:43:00,846 --> 01:43:02,438
嘿
Hey.

978
01:43:06,685 --> 01:43:12,885
你这个混蛋 罗纳德・韦斯莱!
You complete ass, Ronald Weasley!

979
01:43:13,058 --> 01:43:16,721
消失了几个星期才出现 你就只会说"嘿"?
You show up here after weeks, and you say "hey"?

980
01:43:18,931 --> 01:43:21,661
- 我的魔杖呢 哈利? 我的魔杖呢?  - 不知道
- Where's my wand, Harry? Where's my wand?  - I don't know.

981
01:43:21,834 --> 01:43:24,098
- 哈利・波特 把魔杖给我  - 不在我这儿
- Harry Potter, give me my wand.  - I don't have it.

982
01:43:24,270 --> 01:43:28,104
- 他怎么会拿着你的魔杖?  - 不用你管
- How come he's got your wand?  - Never mind why he's got my wand.

983
01:43:30,376 --> 01:43:31,604
那是什么?
What is that?

984
01:43:34,547 --> 01:43:35,571
你销毁它了
You destroyed it.

985
01:43:38,884 --> 01:43:42,843
还有你怎么会带着格兰芬多之剑?
And how is it that you just happen to have the sword of Gryffindor?

986
01:43:43,255 --> 01:43:45,223
说来话长了
It's a long story.

987
01:43:48,394 --> 01:43:52,490
- 别以为这能起什么作用  - 哦 当然不会
- Don't think this changes anything.  - Oh, of course not.

988
01:43:52,665 --> 01:43:55,930
我刚刚只是毁掉了一个见鬼的魂器 这又能起什么作用呢?
I only just destroyed a bloody Horcrux. Why would that change anything?

989
01:43:56,101 --> 01:44:00,162
其实 刚刚离开我就想回来了
Look, I wanted to come back as soon as I left.

990
01:44:00,339 --> 01:44:03,775
- 我只是不知道怎么找到你们  - 是啊 那你是怎么找到的?
- I just didn't know how to find you.  - Yeah, how did you find us?

991
01:44:03,943 --> 01:44:07,003
用这个 这个不仅仅可以熄灭灯光
With this. It doesn't just turn off lights.

992
01:44:07,179 --> 01:44:12,082
我不知道是什么原理 不过圣诞节早晨我睡在一个小酒馆里...
I don't know how it works, but Christmas morning I was sleeping in this little pub...

993
01:44:12,251 --> 01:44:14,685
以防被搜捕队碰到...
keeping away from some Snatchers...

994
01:44:15,120 --> 01:44:16,382
然后我就听到它了
and I heard it.

995
01:44:16,789 --> 01:44:18,222
什么?
It?

996
01:44:19,558 --> 01:44:21,492
一个声音...
A voice...

997
01:44:23,095 --> 01:44:24,289
是你的声音 赫敏...
your voice, Hermione...

998
01:44:25,464 --> 01:44:27,091
由它发出来
coming out of it.

999
01:44:27,266 --> 01:44:31,100
- 我能问问 我究竟说了什么吗?  - 我的名字
- And what exactly did I say, may I ask?  - My name.

1000
01:44:31,704 --> 01:44:33,729
就是我的名字
Just my name.

1001
01:44:34,506 --> 01:44:36,599
就像在我耳边
Like a whisper.

1002
01:44:38,577 --> 01:44:44,573
我就拿起来 打开它 这个小光球就出现了
So I took it, clicked it, and this tiny ball of light appeared.

1003
01:44:45,050 --> 01:44:46,483
而我知道了
And I knew.

1004
01:44:47,052 --> 01:44:51,682
而且非常确定 它飘向我 这个光球...
And sure enough, it floated toward me, the ball of light...

1005
01:44:53,392 --> 01:44:57,590
直扑我的胸口 穿过我 就从这里
went right to my chest, straight through me. Right here.

1006
01:44:58,797 --> 01:45:02,790
我就知道它会带我去我该去的地方 所以我幻影移形...
And I knew it was gonna take me where I needed to go, so I Disapparated...

1007
01:45:02,968 --> 01:45:05,232
就来到了这个山腰
and came to this hillside.

1008
01:45:05,771 --> 01:45:08,296
天色昏暗 我不知道是哪里
It was dark. I had no idea where I was.

1009
01:45:08,841 --> 01:45:11,674
我只希望能碰到你们其中一个
I just hoped that one of you would show yourself.

1010
01:45:12,578 --> 01:45:14,102
然后真就碰到了
And you did.

1011
01:45:31,530 --> 01:45:34,431
我一直很喜欢赫敏造的这些火焰
I've always liked these flames Hermione makes.

1012
01:45:38,470 --> 01:45:41,030
你估计她还会生我的气多久?
How long do you reckon she'll stay mad at me?

1013
01:45:42,574 --> 01:45:45,907
哦 继续讲那个光球触动你心的事情...
Well, just keep talking about that little ball of light touching your heart...

1014
01:45:46,078 --> 01:45:47,511
她就会接受你了
and she'll come round.

1015
01:45:47,680 --> 01:45:50,410
是真的 字字不假
It was true. Every word.

1016
01:45:52,217 --> 01:45:54,583
听起来有点疯狂...
This is gonna sound crazy...

1017
01:45:55,054 --> 01:45:59,423
不过我觉得这是邓布利多把它留给我的原因 这个熄灯器
but I think that's why Dumbledore left it to me, the Deluminator.

1018
01:45:59,925 --> 01:46:04,919
他知道有一天我需要找到回归的路 而赫敏可以指引我
I think he knew that somehow I'd need it to find my way back, and she'd lead me.

1019
01:46:07,800 --> 01:46:10,530
该死的 我刚想到 你需要根魔杖 对吧?
Bloody hell, I just realized, you need a wand, don't you?

1020
01:46:10,703 --> 01:46:13,194
- 是  - 我这有一根
- Yeah.  - I've got one here.

1021
01:46:13,472 --> 01:46:16,066
是黑李木的 十寸长
It's a blackthorn. Ten inches.

1022
01:46:16,241 --> 01:46:19,836
没什么特别的 不过我估计能用
Nothing special, but I reckon it'll do.

1023
01:46:20,279 --> 01:46:23,077
两周前从一个搜捕队员那里抢的
Took if off a Snatcher a couple of weeks ago.

1024
01:46:23,582 --> 01:46:27,416
别告诉赫敏 搜捕队 人员有点复杂
Don't tell Hermione this, but they're a bit dim, Snatchers.

1025
01:46:27,686 --> 01:46:30,621
闻起来这个魔杖的主人应该有巨怪血统
This one was definitely part troll, the smell of him.

1026
01:46:30,789 --> 01:46:31,813
速速变大
Engorgio.

1027
01:46:31,991 --> 01:46:34,152
- 速速缩小!  - 这怎么了?
- Reducio!  - What's going on in there?

1028
01:46:34,326 --> 01:46:35,588
- 没事  - 没事
- Nothing.  - Nothing.

1029
01:46:37,963 --> 01:46:39,590
我们需要谈谈
We need to talk.

1030
01:46:40,399 --> 01:46:41,593
对 好的
Yeah, all right.

1031
01:46:48,574 --> 01:46:52,101
- 我要去见谢诺菲留斯・洛夫古德  - 啊?
- I want to go see Xenophilius Lovegood.  - Sorry?

1032
01:46:53,879 --> 01:46:55,506
看到这个了吗?
See this?

1033
01:46:55,681 --> 01:46:59,549
是邓布利多写给格林德沃的信 看署名
It's a letter Dumbledore wrote to Grindelwald. Look at the signature.

1034
01:47:00,786 --> 01:47:02,981
又是这个标记
It's the mark again.

1035
01:47:03,922 --> 01:47:06,049
不时出现
It keeps cropping up.

1036
01:47:06,225 --> 01:47:10,594
在诗翁彼豆故事集 在戈德里克山谷
In Beedle the Bard, in the graveyard in Godric's Hollow.

1037
01:47:11,430 --> 01:47:13,295
那也有
It was there too.

1038
01:47:13,465 --> 01:47:17,060
- 哪儿?  - 格里戈维奇魔杖店门外
- Where?  - Outside Gregorovitch's Wand Shop.

1039
01:47:17,503 --> 01:47:18,731
可它是什么意思呢?
But what does it mean?

1040
01:47:18,904 --> 01:47:23,705
听我说 反正我们都不知道下一个魂器在哪里...
Look, you've got no idea where the next Horcrux is, and neither do I...

1041
01:47:25,411 --> 01:47:28,346
但这个 这个是有意义的
but this, this means something.

1042
01:47:28,680 --> 01:47:32,081
- 我很肯定  - 对 赫敏说得对
- I'm sure of it.  - Yeah. Hermione's right.

1043
01:47:33,118 --> 01:47:35,211
我们应该去找洛夫古德
We ought to see Lovegood.

1044
01:47:35,721 --> 01:47:39,452
咱们投票吧 同意的举手?
Let's vote on it. Those in favor?

1045
01:48:03,282 --> 01:48:05,910
你不生他气了 是吧?
You're not still mad at him, are you?

1046
01:48:06,218 --> 01:48:08,482
我早习惯了
I'm always mad at him.

1047
01:48:11,256 --> 01:48:12,746
卢娜
Luna.

1048
01:48:12,925 --> 01:48:14,620
卢娜
Luna.

1049
01:48:14,901 --> 01:48:16,834
"勿动飞艇李"

1050
01:48:20,101 --> 01:48:21,834
"唱唱反调"主编 谢・洛夫古德

1051
01:48:22,301 --> 01:48:25,134
"勿动飞艇李"
"Keep off the dirigible plums."

1052
01:48:34,179 --> 01:48:36,875
什么事? 你们是谁?
What is it? Who are you?

1053
01:48:37,182 --> 01:48:38,206
你们要干什么?
What do you want?

1054
01:48:38,383 --> 01:48:42,979
你好 洛夫古德先生 我是哈利・波特 几个月前我们见过
Hello, Mr. Lovegood. I'm Harry Potter. We met a few months ago.

1055
01:48:46,992 --> 01:48:48,892
我们能进去吗?
Could we come in?

1056
01:48:52,664 --> 01:48:55,258
- 卢娜去哪了?  - 卢娜?
- Where is Luna?  - Luna?

1057
01:48:56,535 --> 01:48:58,503
她很快就回来了
She'll be along.

1058
01:49:12,017 --> 01:49:14,076
我能为你做些什么 波特先生?
So how can I help you, Mr. Potter?

1059
01:49:14,920 --> 01:49:17,946
哦 其实...
Well, actually....

1060
01:49:18,957 --> 01:49:23,485
是关于婚礼上你戴在脖子上的一个东西的 是个标记
It was about something you were wearing round your neck at the wedding. A symbol.

1061
01:49:25,030 --> 01:49:26,930
你是说这个?
You mean this?

1062
01:49:27,332 --> 01:49:28,924
是
Yes.

1063
01:49:29,234 --> 01:49:31,099
就是它
That exactly.

1064
01:49:31,770 --> 01:49:35,729
我们想知道的是 它是什么?
What we've wondered is, what is it?

1065
01:49:35,908 --> 01:49:37,739
它是什么?
What is it?

1066
01:49:37,910 --> 01:49:40,879
哦 这是死亡圣器的标记
Well, it's the sign of the Deathly Hallows, of course.

1067
01:49:41,046 --> 01:49:42,138
- 什么?  - 什么?
- The what?  - The what?

1068
01:49:42,314 --> 01:49:44,373
死亡圣器
The Deathly Hallows.

1069
01:49:44,550 --> 01:49:47,644
我估计你们都知道"三兄弟的传说"吧
I assume you're all familiar with "The Tale of the Three Brothers."

1070
01:49:47,819 --> 01:49:49,309
- 知道  - 不知道
- Yes.  - No.

1071
01:49:54,660 --> 01:49:56,423
我这有
I have it in here.

1072
01:50:07,673 --> 01:50:09,300
"曾经有三个兄弟...
"There were once three brothers...

1073
01:50:09,474 --> 01:50:13,877
在黄昏的时候行走在孤独 蜿蜒的路上"
who were traveling along a lonely, winding road at twilight."

1074
01:50:14,046 --> 01:50:16,776
午夜 我妈妈讲的时候说是"午夜"
Midnight. Mom always said "midnight."

1075
01:50:21,787 --> 01:50:25,655
不过"黄昏"也好 其实 更好
But "twilight's" fine. Better, actually.

1076
01:50:27,926 --> 01:50:29,791
要不你来读?
Do you want to read it?

1077
01:50:29,962 --> 01:50:32,157
不了 还是你读得好
No. It's fine.

1078
01:50:34,066 --> 01:50:36,000
"曾经有三个兄弟...
"There were once three brothers...

1079
01:50:36,168 --> 01:50:41,367
在黄昏的时候行走在孤独 蜿蜒的路上
who were traveling along a lonely, winding road at twilight.

1080
01:50:43,242 --> 01:50:48,544
最后 三兄弟来到一条无法逾越的河边
In time, the brothers reached a river too treacherous to pass.

1081
01:50:48,880 --> 01:50:50,745
不过因为精通魔法...
But being learned in the magical arts...

1082
01:50:50,916 --> 01:50:56,081
三个兄弟轻松地挥一挥魔杖创造了一座桥
the three brothers simply waved their wands and made a bridge.

1083
01:50:57,422 --> 01:50:59,515
然而 在他们过河之前...
Before they could cross, however...

1084
01:50:59,691 --> 01:51:03,787
一个戴兜帽的身影挡住了他们的去路
they found their path blocked by a hooded figure.

1085
01:51:04,062 --> 01:51:07,930
是死神 他认为自己被愚弄了
It was Death, and he felt cheated.

1086
01:51:08,100 --> 01:51:11,160
因为通常的行路人都会溺死于河中
Cheated because travelers would normally drown in the river.

1087
01:51:11,336 --> 01:51:13,395
不过死神很奸诈
But Death was cunning.

1088
01:51:14,039 --> 01:51:17,031
他祝贺三兄弟魔力高强...
He pretended to congratulate the three brothers on their magic...

1089
01:51:17,209 --> 01:51:22,476
还说他们因为聪明到可以逃避死亡而获得奖励
and said that each had earned a prize for having been clever enough to evade him.

1090
01:51:23,048 --> 01:51:27,610
大哥要了一根世上最强力的魔杖
The oldest asked for a wand more powerful than any in existence.

1091
01:51:27,786 --> 01:51:32,382
于是死神用附近一棵接骨木的树枝做了一根
So Death fashioned him one from an elder tree that stood nearby.

1092
01:51:33,792 --> 01:51:38,092
二哥决定要变本加厉地羞辱死神...
The second brother decided he wanted to humiliate Death even further...

1093
01:51:38,263 --> 01:51:42,700
要求能让自己的爱人死而复生的能力
and asked for the power to recall loved ones from the grave.

1094
01:51:43,135 --> 01:51:47,435
死神从河中挖起一块石头送给了他
So Death plucked a stone from the river and offered it to him.

1095
01:51:48,173 --> 01:51:52,132
最后 死神转向老三
Finally, Death turned to the third brother.

1096
01:51:53,345 --> 01:51:54,778
这个谦恭的人...
A humble man...

1097
01:51:54,946 --> 01:51:59,144
要求一件可以让他继续前进...
he asked for something that would allow him to go forth from that place...

1098
01:51:59,318 --> 01:52:02,481
而不被死神尾随的东西
without being followed by Death.

1099
01:52:03,588 --> 01:52:09,458
所以死神勉为其难把自己的隐形衣送给了他
And so it was that Death reluctantly handed over his own Cloak of Invisibility.

1100
01:52:12,831 --> 01:52:15,766
最年长的兄弟到了一个遥远的村落...
The first brother traveled to a distant village...

1101
01:52:15,934 --> 01:52:18,027
在那里 凭借手中的老魔杖...
where, with the Elder Wand in hand...

1102
01:52:18,203 --> 01:52:21,969
他杀掉了一个曾经与他争执过的巫师
he killed a wizard with whom he had once quarreled.

1103
01:52:24,176 --> 01:52:27,703
带着老魔杖带给他的魔力酒醉之后...
Drunk with the power that the Elder Wand had given him...

1104
01:52:27,879 --> 01:52:30,973
他吹嘘自己是无敌的
he bragged of his invincibility.

1105
01:52:33,985 --> 01:52:37,443
不过就在当晚 另一个巫师偷走了魔杖...
But that night, another wizard stole the wand...

1106
01:52:37,622 --> 01:52:40,750
保险起见 还割断了他的喉咙
and slit the brother's throat for good measure.

1107
01:52:40,959 --> 01:52:44,395
所以大哥最终还是落在了死神的手里
And so Death took the first brother for his own.

1108
01:52:45,130 --> 01:52:47,098
二哥回到了家园...
The second brother journeyed to his home...

1109
01:52:47,265 --> 01:52:50,234
拿出石头在手中转了三次
where he took the stone and turned it thrice in hand.

1110
01:52:50,402 --> 01:52:54,862
为之欣喜的是 那位他不及迎娶就逝世的姑娘...
To his delight, the girl he'd once hoped to marry before her untimely death...

1111
01:52:55,040 --> 01:52:57,406
出现在了他面前
appeared before him.

1112
01:52:57,909 --> 01:53:03,211
可是 很快她因为得到了永生而变得悲伤冷漠
Yet, soon she turned sad and cold for she did not belong in the mortal world.

1113
01:53:03,382 --> 01:53:05,009
被无望的渴求逼疯之后...
Driven mad with hopeless longing...

1114
01:53:05,183 --> 01:53:08,482
二哥自杀殉情
the second brother killed himself so as to join her.

1115
01:53:09,688 --> 01:53:12,782
他也没有逃脱死神的魔爪
And so Death took the second brother.

1116
01:53:12,958 --> 01:53:14,585
而最小的弟弟...
As for the third brother...

1117
01:53:14,760 --> 01:53:18,992
死神寻找了他很多年却无法找到
Death searched for many years but was never able to find him.

1118
01:53:19,164 --> 01:53:22,065
一直到他年纪很大的时候 这位老三...
Only when he attained a great age did the youngest brother...

1119
01:53:22,234 --> 01:53:26,500
才脱下了隐形衣交给了他的儿子
shed the Cloak of Invisibility and give it to his son.

1120
01:53:27,739 --> 01:53:31,869
然后像老朋友一样问候了死神并跟他一起欣然地离开了...
He then greeted Death as an old friend and went with him gladly...

1121
01:53:32,043 --> 01:53:35,206
与世无争地离世"
departing this life as equals."

1122
01:53:37,282 --> 01:53:41,776
这样你们就明白了 那就是死亡圣器
So there you are. Those are the Deathly Hallows.

1123
01:53:43,188 --> 01:53:46,248
抱歉 先生 我还是不太明白
I'm sorry, sir. I still don't quite understand.

1124
01:53:51,863 --> 01:53:53,956
我的笔放哪了?
Where's that pen I had?

1125
01:54:04,943 --> 01:54:06,205
老魔杖
The Elder Wand.

1126
01:54:07,345 --> 01:54:11,008
世上最强力的魔杖
The most powerful wand ever made.

1127
01:54:21,393 --> 01:54:23,691
复活石
The Resurrection Stone.

1128
01:54:34,573 --> 01:54:38,339
隐形衣
The Cloak of Invisibility.

1129
01:54:40,378 --> 01:54:43,506
放在一起 就组成了死亡圣器
Together, they make the Deathly Hallows.

1130
01:54:43,782 --> 01:54:49,243
放在一起 就能成为死神的主人
Together, they make one master of Death.

1131
01:54:54,459 --> 01:54:58,122
那个标记在戈德里克山谷的一个墓穴上出现过
That mark was on a grave in Godric's Hollow.

1132
01:54:59,231 --> 01:55:01,859
呃 洛夫古德先生 佩弗利尔家族...
Uh, Mr. Lovegood, does the Peverell Family...

1133
01:55:02,033 --> 01:55:03,864
和死亡圣器有什么关系吗?
have anything to do with the Deathly Hallows?

1134
01:55:04,035 --> 01:55:06,868
呃... 呃...
Uh... Uh...

1135
01:55:07,038 --> 01:55:10,804
伊格诺图斯... 请原谅 还有他的兄弟 卡德摩斯和安提俄克...
Ignotus... Excuse me. And his brothers, Cadmus and Antioch...

1136
01:55:10,976 --> 01:55:13,638
被认为是死亡圣器的原始拥有者...
are thought to be the original owners of the Hallows...

1137
01:55:13,812 --> 01:55:18,681
还有这个故事的启示 呃... 呃...
and therefore the inspiration for the story. Uh... Uh...

1138
01:55:18,850 --> 01:55:21,341
不过你们的茶要凉了
But your tea's gone cold.

1139
01:55:22,554 --> 01:55:24,545
我很快回来
I'll be right back.

1140
01:55:24,723 --> 01:55:26,588
咱们下去吧
Let's go down here.

1141
01:55:28,460 --> 01:55:29,950
咱们走吧
Let's get out of here.

1142
01:55:30,128 --> 01:55:32,995
不管是凉是热 我不想再喝那东西了
I'm not drinking any more of that stuff, hot or cold.

1143
01:55:39,304 --> 01:55:41,272
谢谢 先生
Thank you, sir.

1144
01:55:42,173 --> 01:55:45,199
- 你忘记水了  - 水?
- You forgot the water.  - Water?

1145
01:55:45,377 --> 01:55:46,810
泡茶的
For the tea.

1146
01:55:46,978 --> 01:55:49,538
有...? 我有吗?
Did...? Did I?

1147
01:55:51,483 --> 01:55:53,644
我可真傻
How silly of me.

1148
01:55:55,253 --> 01:55:57,517
没关系的 我们真的该走了
It's no matter. We really should be going anyway.

1149
01:55:57,689 --> 01:55:59,748
不 不行!
No, you can't!

1150
01:56:03,962 --> 01:56:05,657
先生?
Sir?

1151
01:56:13,038 --> 01:56:15,632
你们是我唯一的希望
You're my only hope.

1152
01:56:19,511 --> 01:56:23,880
我写的那些东西 惹怒了他们
They were angry, you see, about what I'd been writing.

1153
01:56:26,918 --> 01:56:29,045
所以他们带走了她
So they took her.

1154
01:56:30,522 --> 01:56:33,286
他们抓走了卢娜
They took my Luna.

1155
01:56:34,993 --> 01:56:36,620
我的卢娜
My Luna.

1156
01:56:49,107 --> 01:56:52,008
可是他们真正要找的是你
But it's really you they want.

1157
01:56:54,245 --> 01:56:56,304
先生 什么人抓了她?
Who took her, sir?

1158
01:57:01,453 --> 01:57:02,715
伏地魔
Voldemort.

1159
01:57:13,365 --> 01:57:15,663
停手! 我抓到他了!
Stop! I've got him!

1160
01:57:32,951 --> 01:57:36,853
这个背信弃义的混蛋 难道我们就没有人可以信任了吗?
That treacherous little bleeder. Is there no one we can trust?

1161
01:57:37,022 --> 01:57:39,320
因为他支持我所以他们绑架了卢娜
They kidnapped her because he supported me.

1162
01:57:39,491 --> 01:57:41,618
他只是绝望所致
He was just desperate.

1163
01:57:42,160 --> 01:57:44,355
我来施法
I'll do the enchantments.

1164
01:57:56,041 --> 01:57:57,474
你好啊 美人儿
Hello, beautiful.

1165
01:58:02,947 --> 01:58:06,576
哦 别愣着了 抓住他们
Well, don't hang about, snatch them.

1166
01:59:17,822 --> 01:59:19,312
哈利
Harry.

1167
01:59:19,491 --> 01:59:22,460
告诉我 格林德沃 告诉我它在哪
Tell me, Grindelwald. Tell me where it is.

1168
01:59:23,061 --> 01:59:27,122
格林德沃 格林德沃 格林德沃
Grindelwald. Grindelwald. Grindelwald.

1169
01:59:27,866 --> 01:59:31,324
你好 汤姆 我知道你早晚会来...
Hello, Tom. I knew you would come one day...

1170
01:59:31,803 --> 01:59:35,762
不过你也肯定知道我没有你要的东西了
but surely you must know I no longer have what you seek.

1171
01:59:36,407 --> 01:59:39,433
- 告诉我 格林德沃 告诉我它在哪  - 哈... 哈... 哈
- Tell me, Grindelwald. Tell me where it is.  - Ha... ha... ha.

1172
01:59:39,611 --> 01:59:40,976
告诉我归谁所有
Tell me who possesses it.

1173
01:59:41,179 --> 01:59:46,276
老魔杖当然陪他长眠...
The Elder Wand lies with him, of course...

1174
01:59:46,451 --> 01:59:48,715
深埋入土
buried in the earth.

1175
01:59:49,654 --> 01:59:50,985
邓布利多
Dumbledore.

1176
02:00:00,031 --> 02:00:01,896
圣器真的存在...
The Hallows exist...

1177
02:00:02,066 --> 02:00:05,866
不过他只在寻找其中之一 最后一件 他知道在哪里
but he's only after one of them, the last one. He knows where it is.

1178
02:00:06,037 --> 02:00:09,871
今夜结束之前他就能够据为己有 神秘人拿到了老魔杖
He's gonna have it by the end of the night. You... Know... Who's found the Elder Wand.

1179
02:00:10,041 --> 02:00:12,509
- 别碰她 啊!  - 放开他
- Don't touch her. Unh!  - Leave him.

1180
02:00:12,677 --> 02:00:13,939
你的男朋友如果不识时务的话...
Your boyfriend will get worse than that...

1181
02:00:14,112 --> 02:00:15,238
放开我
Get off me.

1182
02:00:15,413 --> 02:00:18,143
会比这样还难受的
if he doesn't learn to behave himself.

1183
02:00:21,386 --> 02:00:22,876
你怎么回事 丑八怪?
What happened to you, ugly?

1184
02:00:24,589 --> 02:00:26,454
不 不是说你
No, not you.

1185
02:00:27,859 --> 02:00:30,919
- 你叫什么?  - 达力 弗农・达力
- What's your name?  - Dudley. Vernon Dudley.

1186
02:00:31,095 --> 02:00:33,290
检查一下
Check it.

1187
02:00:34,899 --> 02:00:37,231
还有你 亲爱的...
And you, my lovely...

1188
02:00:40,538 --> 02:00:42,529
你叫什么?
what do they call you?

1189
02:00:43,975 --> 02:00:48,036
佩内洛・克里瓦特 混血
Penelope Clearwater, half-blood.

1190
02:00:51,149 --> 02:00:53,083
这里没有弗农・达力
There's no Vernon Dudley on here.

1191
02:00:54,152 --> 02:00:57,383
你听到了吗 丑八怪? 名单证明你在撒谎
Did you hear that, ugly? The list says you're lying.

1192
02:00:57,555 --> 02:00:59,785
为什么隐瞒身份?
How come you don't want us to know who you are?

1193
02:00:59,958 --> 02:01:02,620
名单是错的 我告诉你我是谁了
The list's wrong. I told you who I am.

1194
02:01:18,576 --> 02:01:20,669
计划改变
Change of plan.

1195
02:01:21,746 --> 02:01:25,011
这些人不带去魔法部了
We're not taking this lot to the Ministry.

1196
02:02:04,689 --> 02:02:08,318
带德拉科来
Get Draco.

1197
02:02:12,797 --> 02:02:14,355
怎么样?
Well?

1198
02:02:17,468 --> 02:02:21,996
- 我不确定  - 德拉科 近点看 孩子
- I can't be sure.  - Draco. Look closely, son.

1199
02:02:23,007 --> 02:02:28,070
如果由我们把波特交给黑魔王...
If we are the ones to hand Potter over to the Dark Lord...

1200
02:02:28,246 --> 02:02:33,479
一切都会被原谅的 一切都会重归以往 明白吗?
everything would be forgiven. All would be as it was, you understand?

1201
02:02:33,651 --> 02:02:37,781
噢 马尔福先生 我希望 别忘记是谁抓到他的
Now, we won't be forgetting who actually caught him, I hope, Mr. Malfoy.

1202
02:02:37,956 --> 02:02:40,390
你在我家也敢这样跟我讲话?
You dare to talk to me like that in my own house?

1203
02:02:40,558 --> 02:02:42,355
卢修斯
Lucius.

1204
02:02:45,263 --> 02:02:49,097
别害羞 宝贝 过来
Don't be shy, sweetie. Come over.

1205
02:02:50,601 --> 02:02:55,368
如果这不是波特 德拉科 我们却把他请来 他会杀光我们的
Now, if this isn't who we think it is, Draco, and we call him, he'll kill us all.

1206
02:02:55,540 --> 02:02:58,338
我们需要非常确定
We need to be absolutely sure.

1207
02:02:58,643 --> 02:02:59,632
他的脸怎么了?
What's wrong with his face?

1208
02:02:59,811 --> 02:03:01,540
对啊 他的脸怎么了?
Yes, what is wrong with his face?

1209
02:03:01,713 --> 02:03:02,907
抓到他的时候就是这样
He came to us like that.

1210
02:03:03,081 --> 02:03:05,049
我估计 是他在树林里搞的
Something he picked up in the forest, I reckon.

1211
02:03:05,216 --> 02:03:08,913
或者是中了蜇人咒 是你干的吗 亲爱的?
Or ran into a Stinging Jinx. Was it you, dearie?

1212
02:03:14,025 --> 02:03:16,789
把她的魔杖给我 我们就能知道她最后用的咒语是什么了
Give me her wand. We'll see what her last spell was.

1213
02:03:18,062 --> 02:03:20,223
哈 肯定是你
Ah. Got you.

1214
02:03:24,035 --> 02:03:25,764
那是什么?
What is that?

1215
02:03:27,705 --> 02:03:29,297
你这从哪来的?
Where'd you get that from?

1216
02:03:29,474 --> 02:03:32,966
我们抓到她的时候从她袋子里找到的 现在算是我的了
It was in her bag when we searched her. Reckon it's mine now.

1217
02:03:36,714 --> 02:03:38,045
你疯了?
Are you mad?

1218
02:03:46,357 --> 02:03:49,190
滚! 快滚!
Go! Get out!

1219
02:03:54,832 --> 02:03:58,996
西茜 把小伙子们关进地牢
Cissy, put the boys in the cellar.

1220
02:03:59,170 --> 02:04:04,540
我要跟这个谈谈 女人跟女人的谈话
I want to have a little conversation with this one, girl-to-girl.

1221
02:04:13,584 --> 02:04:16,678
我们怎么办? 我们不能把赫敏一个人丢给她
What are we gonna do? We can't leave Hermione alone with her.

1222
02:04:16,854 --> 02:04:18,219
罗恩?
Ron?

1223
02:04:23,428 --> 02:04:24,986
哈利?
Harry?

1224
02:04:30,701 --> 02:04:32,259
卢娜?
Luna?

1225
02:04:32,870 --> 02:04:37,034
这把剑应该在古灵阁我的金库里 你怎么拿到的?
That sword is meant to be in my vault at Gringotts. How did you get it?

1226
02:04:37,208 --> 02:04:40,336
你们还拿了我什么东西?!
What else did you and your friends take from my vault?!

1227
02:04:40,511 --> 02:04:45,881
我什么都没拿 真的 我什么都没拿
I didn't take anything. Please. I didn't take anything.

1228
02:04:46,050 --> 02:04:47,574
我不相信
I don't believe it.

1229
02:04:53,157 --> 02:04:54,249
我们要采取措施
We have to do something.

1230
02:04:54,425 --> 02:04:58,452
出不去 我们都试过了 都被施了魔法
There's no way out of here. We've tried everything. It's enchanted.

1231
02:04:58,629 --> 02:05:01,325
- 求你! 求你!  - 闭嘴!
- Please! please!  - Shut up!

1232
02:05:01,499 --> 02:05:03,296
你流血了 哈利
You're bleeding, Harry.

1233
02:05:03,468 --> 02:05:05,493
你袜子里装这东西真有意思
That's a curious thing to keep in your sock.

1234
02:05:14,745 --> 02:05:15,871
帮帮我们
Help us.

1235
02:05:21,652 --> 02:05:23,552
- 放了她  - 闭嘴 退后
- Let her go.  - Shut up. Get back.

1236
02:05:24,889 --> 02:05:29,087
你 妖精 跟我走
You, goblin, come with me.

1237
02:05:48,746 --> 02:05:50,236
- 啊!  - 多比?
- Aah!  - Dobby?

1238
02:05:51,115 --> 02:05:52,514
你来干什么?
What are you doing here?

1239
02:05:52,683 --> 02:05:54,947
多比当然是来救哈利・波特的
Dobby has come to rescue Harry Potter, of course.

1240
02:05:55,119 --> 02:05:57,587
多比会永远支持哈利・波特
Dobby will always be there for Harry Potter.

1241
02:05:57,755 --> 02:06:01,350
在这里你可以幻影移形? 你能带我们一起走吗?
You can Apparate in and out of this room? Could you take us with you?

1242
02:06:01,526 --> 02:06:03,289
当然 先生 我是个精灵
Of course, sir. I'm an elf.

1243
02:06:04,095 --> 02:06:05,960
可以的
Works for me.

1244
02:06:06,197 --> 02:06:08,563
多比 我要你带着卢娜和奥利凡德先生...
Dobby, I want you to take Luna and Mr. Ollivander...

1245
02:06:08,733 --> 02:06:11,167
去丁沃斯郊外的贝壳小屋
Shell Cottage on the outskirts of Tinworth.

1246
02:06:11,536 --> 02:06:12,560
放心吧
Trust me.

1247
02:06:13,371 --> 02:06:14,804
随时可以 先生
Whenever you're ready, sir.

1248
02:06:15,506 --> 02:06:18,202
先生? 我很喜欢她
Sir? I like her very much.

1249
02:06:23,147 --> 02:06:26,446
10秒之后在上面等我
Meet me at the top of the stairs in 10 seconds.

1250
02:06:35,526 --> 02:06:37,289
噢
Ow.

1251
02:06:42,700 --> 02:06:44,930
有谁缺魔杖吗?
Who gets his wand?

1252
02:06:47,672 --> 02:06:51,665
我只问你一遍 妖精
I'm only going to ask you once more, goblin.

1253
02:06:51,842 --> 02:06:55,243
回答之前三思 再三思
Think very, very carefully before you answer.

1254
02:06:55,613 --> 02:06:57,171
我不知道
I don't know.

1255
02:06:57,348 --> 02:07:00,545
你不知道? 你怎么不尽职?
You don't know? Why weren't you doing your job?

1256
02:07:00,718 --> 02:07:03,949
谁进入了我的金库?
Who got into my vault?

1257
02:07:05,223 --> 02:07:09,660
谁偷的? 谁偷走的? 嗯?
Who stole it? Who stole it? Well?

1258
02:07:09,827 --> 02:07:13,854
当我最后一次离开你的金库的时候 剑还在那
When I was last in your vault, the sword was there.

1259
02:07:14,501 --> 02:07:15,999
泥巴种

1260
02:07:16,634 --> 02:07:19,831
哦 那么 是它自己跑出来的了
Oh, well then, perhaps it just walked out on its own then.

1261
02:07:20,004 --> 02:07:22,438
没有比古灵阁更安全的地方
There is no place safer than Gringotts.

1262
02:07:22,607 --> 02:07:24,040
骗子!
Liar!

1263
02:07:25,977 --> 02:07:29,378
庆幸吧 妖精
Consider yourself lucky, goblin.

1264
02:07:31,816 --> 02:07:35,217
她就没有你这么幸运
The same won't be said for this one.

1265
02:07:35,386 --> 02:07:37,149
该死
Like hell.

1266
02:07:37,888 --> 02:07:39,116
除你武器!
Expelliarmus!

1267
02:07:40,558 --> 02:07:41,650
昏昏倒地
Stupefy.

1268
02:07:45,796 --> 02:07:47,161
住手!
Stop!

1269
02:07:48,332 --> 02:07:49,890
丢掉魔杖
Drop your wands.

1270
02:07:52,770 --> 02:07:53,794
我说了 丢掉!
I said, drop them!

1271
02:07:55,306 --> 02:07:56,739
捡起来 德拉科 快
Pick them up, Draco, now.

1272
02:07:57,608 --> 02:08:01,738
哦 哦 哦 看看这是谁
Well, well, well, look what we have here.

1273
02:08:03,347 --> 02:08:04,837
是哈利・波特
It's Harry Potter.

1274
02:08:05,616 --> 02:08:11,987
他又阳光回来了 正好赶上送给黑魔王
He's all bright and shiny and new again, just in time for the Dark Lord.

1275
02:08:12,156 --> 02:08:14,181
通知他
Call him.

1276
02:08:17,928 --> 02:08:19,725
通知他
Call him.

1277
02:08:54,932 --> 02:08:56,763
昏昏倒地!
Stupefy!

1278
02:08:57,535 --> 02:08:59,230
愚蠢的精灵
Stupid elf.

1279
02:08:59,403 --> 02:09:02,429
- 你差点杀了我  - 多比不想杀人
- You could've killed me.  - Dobby never meant to kill.

1280
02:09:02,606 --> 02:09:06,633
多比只想致残或者重伤
Dobby only meant to maim or seriously injure.

1281
02:09:08,946 --> 02:09:12,279
你竟敢夺走一个巫师的魔杖?
How dare you take a witch's wand?

1282
02:09:12,450 --> 02:09:15,442
你竟敢反抗主人?
How dare you defy your masters?

1283
02:09:15,619 --> 02:09:18,747
多比没有主人
Dobby has no master.

1284
02:09:18,923 --> 02:09:21,414
多比是自由的精灵
Dobby is a free elf.

1285
02:09:21,592 --> 02:09:26,552
而且多比来拯救哈利・波特和他的朋友们
And Dobby has come to save Harry Potter and his friends.

1286
02:09:56,394 --> 02:09:58,055
赫敏
Hermione.

1287
02:09:58,229 --> 02:10:00,720
你没事了 我们安全了
You're all right. We're safe.

1288
02:10:00,898 --> 02:10:02,923
我们安全了
We're all safe.

1289
02:10:03,801 --> 02:10:05,996
哈利・波特
Harry Potter.

1290
02:10:09,740 --> 02:10:11,571
多比
Dobby.

1291
02:10:22,086 --> 02:10:25,146
多比 不 你... 坚持住
Dobby. No, just... Hold on.

1292
02:10:25,322 --> 02:10:29,656
坚持 坚持住 好吗?
Hold on. Look, just hold on, okay?

1293
02:10:29,827 --> 02:10:31,886
我们会救你的
We'll fix you.

1294
02:10:32,329 --> 02:10:35,059
赫敏会有办法
Hermione will have something.

1295
02:10:35,232 --> 02:10:37,564
在你袋子里 是吧赫敏?
In your bag. Hermione?

1296
02:10:39,203 --> 02:10:40,534
赫敏?
Hermione?

1297
02:10:42,740 --> 02:10:45,868
有什么? 帮帮我
What is it? Help me.

1298
02:10:48,446 --> 02:10:51,574
真是个美丽的地方...
Such a beautiful place...

1299
02:10:53,751 --> 02:10:56,015
跟朋友们在一起
to be with friends.

1300
02:10:57,822 --> 02:11:03,226
多比很高兴跟他的朋友...
Dobby is happy to be with his friend...

1301
02:11:05,629 --> 02:11:08,063
哈利・波特在一起
Harry Potter.

1302
02:11:28,853 --> 02:11:31,253
我们让他瞑目吧
We should close his eyes.

1303
02:11:31,489 --> 02:11:33,514
你觉得呢?
Don't you think?

1304
02:11:38,629 --> 02:11:40,028
好了
There.

1305
02:11:40,498 --> 02:11:42,932
这样他就可以安息了
Now he could be sleeping.

1306
02:11:58,249 --> 02:12:00,308
我要埋葬他
I want to bury him.

1307
02:12:01,352 --> 02:12:04,913
传统的 不用魔法
Properly. Without magic.

1308
02:13:14,815 --> 02:13:22,034
 
1309
02:13:22,135 --> 02:13:37,094
 


